Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}进来{\r}\NCome in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}斯班塞先生 很抱歉打扰你{\r}\NMr Spencer. Mr Spencer, I hate to bother you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有两个男人来过{\r}\Nbut I thought you'd like to know there were two men here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.23,0:02:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说是找你的{\r}\NTwo men askin' for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一个年轻人 另一个老些{\r}\NA young man and a kind of older man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我说你不在 他们好像不高兴{\r}\NThey was sorry you wasn't in. I said you wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他们有说会再来吗? - 没说但我想他们会再来的{\r}\N- Did they say they'd be back? - They didn't say, but I think they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}刚才我出去买东西的时候 看见他们在拐角那里等着{\r}\NJust now, when I had to go to the store, I seen them standing there at the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也许我应该让他们进来 但不能打扰你{\r}\NMaybe I shoulda let them in, only you said not to disturb you -
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:03:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是吗? - 我觉得他们会再来的{\r}\N- Yes. - And I'm sure They'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你样子看上去很疲惫啊{\r}\NYou look kinda tired to me, and that's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有些头疼吗?{\r}\NYou got a headache or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想你应该好好休息一下了{\r}\NI think maybe you need a real rest. That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}斯班塞先生 你不该把钱到处放{\r}\NWhy, Mr Spencer. You oughtn't to leave all that money lying around like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看到这样我觉得很不自然{\r}\NOh, it makes me nervous to see money lying around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}世界上不是 所有人都是诚实的{\r}\NEverybody in the world ain't honest, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但你可以相信我 我是很诚实的{\r}\NThough I must say I haven't had much trouble that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你的一些朋友打电话来了 还叫我不要告诉你{\r}\NThose friends of yours told me not to mention they'd called.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说想给你一个惊喜 但我还是要说一声{\r}\NWanted to surprise you. But I thought you'd like to know somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是啊当然了如果他们 再来就让他们进来吧{\r}\NYes, yes. Of course. If they come back, you may show them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有一位叫马丁太太的人 很有意思{\r}\NYes. You know, Mrs Martin, it's very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们并不是我的朋友 还没见过我{\r}\NThey aren't exactly friends of mine. They've never seen me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 很奇怪是吧? - 的确很奇怪{\r}\N- That's odd, isn't it? - 'Tis odd, like you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}既然我在这里 我就要见他们{\r}\NAnd now that I'm here, I'll have to meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}甚至要出去见他们{\r}\NI may even go out and meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但现在还不是时候{\r}\NAnd then again, I may not. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你继续睡吧 我把窗布拉下来{\r}\NYou go ahead with your nap. I'll pull down the blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们知道什么? 你们只是在作势{\r}\NWhat do you know? You're bluffing. You've nothing on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}邮局吗? 我要发一封电报...{\r}\NHello, Postal Union? I want to send a telegram
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}给加州圣罗莎的 约瑟夫.牛顿{\r}\Nto Mrs Joseph Newton in Santa Rosa, California.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}下面是内容 准备好了吗?{\r}\NHere's the message. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很想念你们句号{\r}\NLonesome for you all. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我就来找你们句号{\r}\NAm coming out to stay with you awhile. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}周四到达 请来接我{\r}\NWill arrive Thursday and try and stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}准确时间稍后告知{\r}\NWill wire exact time later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}祝福所有人...{\r}\NLove to you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}并附上查利叔叔的吻 给小查莉{\r}\Nand a kiss for little Charlie from her Uncle Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没错签名就是查利叔叔{\r}\NThat's right. That's the signature. "Uncle Charlie. "
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的圣罗莎{\r}\NThat's right. Santa Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}加州圣罗莎{\r}\NSanta Rosa, California.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安妮听电话啊{\r}\NAnn! Answer the telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这里是牛顿家{\r}\NNewton's residence. Ann Newton speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢你好汉德森太太 我是安妮{\r}\NOh, hello, Mrs Henderson. This is Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈妈还没回家{\r}\NMother isn't home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.64,0:08:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}电报?我...{\r}\NA telegram? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我找不到铅笔 还是等她回来吧{\r}\NI don't see a pencil, so maybe she better call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我正努力使自己 专注一些...{\r}\NI'm trying to keep my mind free of things that don't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为我在思考许多问题{\r}\Nbecause I have so much to keep on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}数不清的问题{\r}\NInnumerable things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会告诉她回电的 谢谢你{\r}\NI'll have her call back. Thank you for calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再见{\r}\NGoodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安妮你妈妈呢?{\r}\NHello, Ann. Where's your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 她出去了 - 出去了?{\r}\N- She ' s out. - Out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:09:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}邮局的汉德森太太 刚刚打电话来的{\r}\NMrs Henderson just called from the Postal Union Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她说我们收到一封电报{\r}\NShe says we have a telegram.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我本可以记下来的 但我找不到铅笔{\r}\NI would have taken it down, only I couldn't find a pencil. I looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}电报吗?{\r}\NTelegram, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我说过你们的萨拉阿姨 如果领到执照就有麻烦了{\r}\NI knew there'd be trouble if your Aunt Sarah got her driver's licence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 事故地点在哪里? - 我没有记下来{\r}\N- Whereabouts was the accident? - I didn't take notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢那么来一个吻好吗?{\r}\NOh. Then how about a kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那不是很有趣吗? 我是家里最特别的女孩...{\r}\NIsn't that the funniest thing? Here I am, practically a child
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看一些你们都不看的书{\r}\Nand I wouldn't read the things you read.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想那些书 会给你带来恶梦的{\r}\NMm-hm. Well, I guess they'd give you bad dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}恶梦?爸爸你不明白 那些传说和神话...{\r}\NBad dreams? You don't understand, Papa. Mystery stories have done -
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 罗杰呢? - 出去了还有人类的思想...{\r}\N- Where's Roger? - Out. The average mind -
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查莉呢? - 她在房间里思考{\r}\N- Where's Charlie? - Out. No, she's in her room thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别看太多了 对你的眼睛不好{\r}\NWell, don't read too much. You'll ruin your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别看我的书了 你在看什么?{\r}\NAnd leave my book alone. What's that you're reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 艾凡赫 - 噢{\r}\N- Ivanhoe. - Hm? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是谁? - 是我{\r}\N- Who is it? - It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么了? 不舒服吗?{\r}\NWhat's the matter? Don't you feel well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不我很好{\r}\NNo. I'm perfectly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我已经想了很久 然后得出结论我应该放弃{\r}\NI've just been thinking for hours, and I've come to the conclusion I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 只能放弃 - 你要放弃什么?{\r}\N- I simply give up. - What are you going to give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你认为家庭应该是 世界上最美好的事物吗?{\r}\NHave you ever to thought that a family should be the most wonderful thing ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而我们的家庭正趋向分解{\r}\NAnd that this family's just gone to pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是吗? - 当然是了{\r}\N- We have? - Of course we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们只是惯例地生活下去 那种惯例太可怕了{\r}\NWe just sort of go along and nothing happens. We're in a terrible rut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}几个月前我已经在想了 我们的将来会是怎样?{\r}\NIt's been on my mind for months. What's going to be our future?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢查莉别这样 事情不是那么糟糕的{\r}\NOh, come now, Charlie. Things aren't as bad as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 银行一月份已经 给我加薪了   - 钱{\r}\N- The bank gave me a raise last January. - Money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在我说心灵的时候 你怎么可以说到钱呢?{\r}\NHow can you talk about money when I'm talking about souls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们一起吃饭然后睡觉{\r}\NWe eat and sleep and that's about all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}并没有真正的交流{\r}\NWe don't even have any real conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们只是说话 还有工作{\r}\N- We just talk. - And work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}可怜的妈妈 那么辛苦地工作{\r}\NYes. Poor Mother. She works like a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 就像一个佣人 - 她在哪里?{\r}\N- Just like a dog. - Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她出去了 她回来了也是一样地工作{\r}\NShe's out. When she comes back, it'll be the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}做晚餐洗碗然后睡觉 我不明白她怎么可以忍受{\r}\NDinner, then dishes, then bed. I don't see how she stands it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道她是一个很好的女人{\r}\NYou know, she's really a wonderful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.43,0:11:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她不仅仅是一个母亲 我们应该为她做些事情{\r}\NI mean, she's not just a mother. And I think we ought to do something for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你觉得应该吗? - 应该那你认为要做些什么呢?{\r}\N- Don ' t you think we should? - Yeah. What were you thinking of?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢我想不出什么{\r}\NOh, nothing, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想我们只能等待 奇迹出现了{\r}\NI guess we'll just have to wait for a miracle or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢查莉你说得对{\r}\NOh, now, Charlie, you're right. Absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我会想办法... - 噢我不再相信什么好意愿了{\r}\N- I'll figure out some way - - I don't believe in good intentions now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我现在只是等待着奇迹 - 噢查莉{\r}\N- All I'm waiting for now is a miracle. - Oh, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}后楼梯真陡啊{\r}\NThose back stairs are steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么了查莉? 怎么了祖?{\r}\NWhat's the matter, Charlie? What's the matter, Joe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 看来... - 噢我成了唠叨的老太婆了{\r}\N- Well, it seems that, uh - - Oh, I've become a nagging old maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这帽子你答应会扔掉的 但你还戴着它进城里{\r}\NYou went downtown in that awful old hat you'd promised you'd throw away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 妈妈 - 亲爱的我戴什么 帽子有什么紧要吗?{\r}\N- Mama. - Darling, does it matter what hat I wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 妈妈 - 妈妈你怎么让 自己的孩子这样向你大喊呢?{\r}\N- Mama. - Why do you let that child yell at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 如果她... - 我反正都要下去的{\r}\N- If she - - I'm going downstairs, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}祖我进来的时候 你们在谈什么呢?{\r}\NJoe, what were you both talking about when I came in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谈奇迹的事情{\r}\NSomething about a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没什么的 查莉只是心情不太好{\r}\NOh, it's nothing. Charlie ' s a bit under the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她很快就会没事的{\r}\NOh. Well, she ' II be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好了亲爱的快下去吧 不要站在这里{\r}\NWell, come on, dear. Let's go downstairs. No use standing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我去喝一瓶啤酒{\r}\NI'm going to get myself a bottle of beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈妈 我要去发一封电报{\r}\NMother, I'm going downtown and send a telegram.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为什么 你要发电报给谁?{\r}\NWhy, darling, who do you know to send a telegram to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道谁可以来拯救我们{\r}\NI know a wonderful person who'll come and stir us up. Just the one to save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}拯救我们?{\r}\NWhat do you mean, "save us"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在就只有一个人可以做到{\r}\NAll this time, there's been one right person to save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 妈妈查理叔叔的地址是什么? - 查理叔叔?{\r}\N- What's Uncle Charlie's address? - Uncle Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你不是去问他要钱吧? - 当然不是了{\r}\N- You're not going to ask him for money? - Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那对我们没帮助地址呢? 上次我放在...{\r}\NThat wouldn't help us. What's his address?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们知道从药房那里...{\r}\N- The last address I had - - Do you know how many steps it is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走回家要走多少步呢?{\r}\Nto get from here to the drugstore and back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 如果你忘记了, 我就不告诉你{\r}\N- 649. - 649. - If you've forgotten, I won't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我记起来了是费城{\r}\N- I remember. Philadelphia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:13:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你不能无缘无故地叫一个大忙人过来啊{\r}\NYou can't ask a busy man to come all this way for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他会来的, 我的名字是因他而起的{\r}\NHe'll come for me. I'm named after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}此外, 我们是他唯一的亲戚{\r}\NBesides, we're the only relatives he has in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果从第四街走回来, 就是802步{\r}\NIf you come all the way up Fourth Street, it's 802.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 妈妈你猜猜? - 我没时间去猜{\r}\N- Mama, guess what? - I have no time for guessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你头发上面的是什么?{\r}\NWhat's that thing in your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要告诉你的 要猜的话有趣一点{\r}\NWell, I'll tell you anyway, even though I think it's nicer when people guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}汉德森太太叫你打电话 给邮局我们有一封电报{\r}\NMrs Henderson said to call her at the telegraph office. We have a telegram.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安妮你不应该 把东西放在耳朵后面的{\r}\NAnn, I don't think you ought to put things behind your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 会进耳朵里面的 - 艾玛安妮说我们有电报{\r}\N- Something might get into your ear. - Emmy, Ann says we have a telegram.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想你应该去查清楚 可能有人病了{\r}\NI think you ought to find out about it. Somebody might be sick or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 汉德森太太没有读出来... 因为我找不到铅笔{\r}\NMrs Henderson didn't read the telegram because I couldn't find a pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}等我有了屋子之后 我会在周围放满铅笔{\r}\NWhen I have a house, it's going to be full of well-sharpened pencils.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 汉德森太太有说是哪里来的电报吗? - 没有{\r}\N- Did Mrs Henderson say who it's from? - No, she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她应该说电报从哪里来的{\r}\NShe might have said who it was from.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 安妮那是我的椅子啊 - 我会问清楚的{\r}\NCome on, Ann. That's my chair. I'll call up and find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们静一会好吗{\r}\NIf you will be quiet just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你好请接181好吗?{\r}\NHello. 181, please. I wonder who it can be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:14:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没什么就是181{\r}\NOh, nothing, Operator. Just 181.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 如果是我姐姐的... - 喂?{\r}\N- If that's from my sister - - Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}汉德森太太吗? 我是艾玛{\r}\NMrs Henderson? This is Emma Newton.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安妮说我有一封电报{\r}\NAnn says you have a telegram for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈妈你不用那么大声的{\r}\N- Mama, you don't have to shout. - Ssh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}爸爸妈妈 好像没用过电话一样{\r}\NReally, Papa. You'd think Mama had never seen a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她这样很不科学{\r}\NShe makes no allowance for science.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}认为用声音 就可以压倒听众{\r}\NShe thinks she has to cover the distance by sheer lungpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真好啊是周四吗?{\r}\NWhy, how wonderful. Thursday, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}似乎有人就要来了{\r}\NLooks like somebody's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 谁要来啊妈妈? - 那真是最大的惊喜啊{\r}\N- Who's coming, Ma? - Well, it's the most wonderful surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是我的弟弟就是他{\r}\NIt's my brother, you know. My younger brother. The baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是啊他被宠坏了家里 最小的一个总会被宠坏的{\r}\NYes, of course, a little spoiled. Families always spoil the youngest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这真是太好了{\r}\NWell, it's just simply wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢你汉德森太太{\r}\NThanks most awfully, Mrs Henderson.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好了{\r}\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你猜是谁? 查理就要来了{\r}\NWhat do you think? Charles is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 谁? - 你们的查理叔叔{\r}\N- Who? - Your Uncle Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查理叔叔?{\r}\NDid you say "Charles"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们的查莉正去给他发电报呢 - 她为什么那样做呢?{\r}\NAnd our Charlie's sending him a telegram. Now, what made her think to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你好啊查莉 你妈妈刚打电话来了{\r}\NHello, Charlie. I just called your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你妈妈的电报 - 是吗?{\r}\N- Telegram for your mother. - Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}本来让比尔送过去的 你现在可以拿走了{\r}\NGonna send that by Bill Forest, but you can take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 谢谢 - 是你叔叔的{\r}\NThanks. From your uncle. The spoiled one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我叔叔? 查理叔叔?{\r}\NMy uncle? My Uncle Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是的{\r}\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}汉德森太太 你相信心灵感应吗?{\r}\NMrs Henderson, do you believe in telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢那是我的工作啊{\r}\NWell, I ought to. That's my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不是邮件 是心灵感应啊{\r}\NOh, not telegraphy. Mental telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那就是说... 你想到了一些事情{\r}\NLike... well, suppose you have a thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}假设你想到了一个 和你很相似的人{\r}\Nand suppose the thought's about someone you're in tune with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}然后那个与你 相隔千里的人回应你{\r}\NThen across miles, that person knows what you're thinking and answers you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 就是心灵感应 - 我不知道你在说什么{\r}\N- And it's all mental. - I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我只会收发邮件{\r}\NI only send telegrams the normal way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他听见我的{\r}\NHe heard me. He heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 奥提斯先生? - 什么?{\r}\N- Mr Otis? Mr Otis? - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就到圣罗莎了 你应该准备一下{\r}\NYou're almost in Santa Rosa. Want to be ready when you get into Santa Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我准备好了谢谢 - 那我帮你拿行李出来{\r}\N- I'm ready now. Thanks. - Then I'll get all your bags out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你觉得怎么了 奥提斯先生?- 很好{\r}\N- How you feelin', Mr Otis? - Pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只是有点虚弱 其他都很好{\r}\NA little weak but pretty well on the whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哦{\r}\NMm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哈里告诉他你是医生吧{\r}\NHarry, tell the porter you're a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看看他有什么问题 你也许可以帮他的{\r}\NAsk if there's anything you can do. Maybe you can help that poor soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我正在休假啊搬运工 我丈夫是医生你去问问他...{\r}\N- I'm on my vacation. - My husband's a doctor and if there's -
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不必了夫人 他不想见任何人{\r}\NNo, Ma'am. He's a very sick man. Won't see anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们上车之后就没见他出来{\r}\NI haven't set eyes on him myself since we first got on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你脸色也不太好啊{\r}\NWell, you don ' t look very well either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:17:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}到了孩子们出来吧{\r}\NAh, here we are. Come on, children.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把门关好对了{\r}\NClose the door, there. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你就是... - 查理{\r}\N- Oh, are you - - Charlie. Young Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}小查莉我开始 还认不出来呢我以为你病了{\r}\NAt first, I didn't know you. I thought you were sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.18,0:18:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 病了? - 你没病的{\r}\N- Sick? - You aren't sick, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}爸爸他在这里!{\r}\NLook, Pop! Here he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查理叔叔你没病啊 真有点奇怪{\r}\NWhy, Uncle Charlie, you're not sick. That was the funniest thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我病了?祖你好啊 - 你好查理{\r}\N- Me, sick? Well, Joe, how are you? - Alright, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们好啊罗杰安妮 应该认不出我了{\r}\NRoger. Hello, Ann. I bet you don't remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我隐约记起 你样子好像不同了{\r}\NI remember you sort of. You look different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们赶快回去吧 艾玛就做好晚餐了{\r}\NWell, we better get started. Emma's got the dinner almost ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她不能来车站 晚餐第一啊{\r}\NI couldn't persuade her to come to the station. Dinner came first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 罗杰拿行李我来吧查理 - 谢谢祖{\r}\N- Roger, get the bags. I'll take that. - Thank you, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}到了来吧{\r}\NThat's it. Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}罗杰 拿这些行李{\r}\NCome on, Roger, get these bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢对你来说真的不重吗?{\r}\NYou, uh, sure that isn't too heavy for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没什么 我喜欢搬东西的{\r}\NOh, no. It's nothing. I love to carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}艾玛别动{\r}\NEmma. Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}站在那里 你不像是艾玛.牛顿{\r}\NStanding there, you don't look like Emma Newton.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你还是艾玛.奥克里 住在明尼苏达州 圣保罗市本翰大街46号{\r}\NYou look like Emma Spencer Oakley of 46 Burnham Street, St Paul, Minnesota.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那一区最漂亮的女孩! - 查理{\r}\N- The prettiest girl on the block. - Charles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉妈妈车站里 只有叔叔一个人下车{\r}\NMama, nobody got off the train but Uncle Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 让我看看你 - 只有我们在那里接人{\r}\N- Let me look at you. - There was only us meeting somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很难想像你会来这里{\r}\N- To think you could take the time off. - There was only one bed made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 噢查理你来了真好 - 艾玛别哭啊{\r}\N- It's so wonderful to have you here. - Emmy, Emmy, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你在想起 本翰大街46号吧{\r}\NAnd imagine your thinking of 46 Burnham Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我很多年没想过那里了{\r}\NI haven't thought of that funny old street in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我一直想起过去那些 美好的事情艾玛他样子怎么了?{\r}\NI keep remembering those things. All the old things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还是没变对吧?{\r}\NEmmy, how's he look? Same old Charles, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}罗杰安妮 去拿那些包{\r}\NRoger, Ann, get these other bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你就住在查莉的房间里{\r}\NYou have Charlie's room right here at the head of the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}艾玛本想安妮搬出来的 但查理说你在这里会舒服些{\r}\NEmmy wanted to move Ann, but Charlie thought you'd be more comfortable here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来吧罗杰{\r}\NCome on, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 别把帽子放在床上啊 - 你也迷信吗祖?{\r}\N- Ah-ah! Don't put the hat on the bed. - Superstitious, Joe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不但我不想 带来什么麻烦事{\r}\NNo, but I don't believe in inviting trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那游艇并不是最大的 但在图书馆里有壁炉...{\r}\NIt wasn't the biggest yacht in the world, but it had a fireplace in the library
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}酒吧的面板都是桃木做的{\r}\Nand the bar was panelled in bleached mahogany.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只要按那个键...好了 不说我的{\r}\NYou pushed a button and... What am I talking about? That's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说说你们吧{\r}\NLet's talk about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉这是我见你 穿过的最漂亮的裙子啊{\r}\NCharlie, that's the prettiest dress I ever saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也这样认为啊{\r}\NI think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查理你忘记了吗?{\r}\NWhy, Charles, don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}忘记?忘记什么?{\r}\NRemember? Remember what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查理叔叔 这是你寄给我的是吗?{\r}\N- Why, Uncle Charlie, you sent it to me. - I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是啊看我 总是忘了一些事情{\r}\NWell, say, I've been sitting here all this time forgetting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.96,0:21:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安妮罗杰{\r}\NAnn. Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 看看你们 - 祖不知道你有没有{\r}\N- Look at that. Oh, dear now. - Joe. Don't know whether you had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不用给我买礼物吧 给孩子们就可以了{\r}\NYou didn't have to think of me, Charles. Presents for the children are alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢...我还没有过 一苹腕表呢{\r}\NSay... I've never had a wristwatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}银行里的同事 还说我是运动型呢{\r}\NFellows at the bank'll think I'm quite a sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}艾玛你有两份 一新一旧{\r}\NI have two for you, Emmy. One old and one new.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢查理 是什么呢?{\r}\NOh, Charles. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:21:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你真是...{\r}\N- You shouldn't have. Really. No. - Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢查理{\r}\NOh, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.33,0:22:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}多么漂亮啊{\r}\NOh, how... beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我总想有一件的{\r}\NOh, I've-I've always wanted one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是啊妈妈 你应该有一件的{\r}\NOh, Mother, it's exactly right. It's what you should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.05,0:22:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看看{\r}\NLook, Emmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查理你一直带在身边{\r}\NCharles. You've had these all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是啊艾玛很多年了{\r}\NMm-hm. All along, Emmy. All these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.69,0:22:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}无论去哪里 都存放在保险箱{\r}\NSafe in a deposit box, no matter where I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢是外公和外婆吗?{\r}\NOh. Grandpa and Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}1888年{\r}\N1888.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.03,0:22:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}53年前了{\r}\N53 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.28,0:22:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他们很和蔼对吗? - 噢她很美啊{\r}\NAren't they sweet? My, she was pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.95,0:22:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在那个时候 每个人都很美的{\r}\NEverybody was sweet and pretty then. The whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.58,0:22:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一个精彩的世界 不像现在的那样{\r}\NA wonderful world. Not like the world today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.33,0:22:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不像现在的世界{\r}\NNot like the world now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那时候年轻真好{\r}\NIt was great to be young then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.71,0:22:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们现在很开心啊 看看大家{\r}\NWe're all happy now, Uncle Charlie. Look at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们第一次同时那么开心 - 现在是你的礼物了查莉{\r}\N- And we're all happy at the same time. - Now, for your present, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.09,0:23:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢我什么都不需要 现在已经很满足了{\r}\NOh, I don't want anything. Right now, I have enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.68,0:23:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你来之前 我以为我需要很多东西{\r}\NBefore you came, I didn't think I had anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.72,0:23:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但现在我觉得不需要了{\r}\Nbut now I don't want another thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 她傻了 - 她并不是傻了{\r}\N- She's crazy. - She doesn't mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.82,0:23:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她其实是在假装 像小说里面的女孩那样{\r}\NIf you ask me, I think she's putting on, like girls in books.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.40,0:23:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}口里说不需要 而后来就什么都想要{\r}\NThe ones that say they don't want anything always get more in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.57,0:23:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 她是这样想的 - 她不傻啊{\r}\N- That's what she's hoping. - She's not crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.83,0:23:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在班里她是最聪明的{\r}\NThe smartest girl in her class at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.91,0:23:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 独自一人在辩论赛中赢了里奇门中学辩论队 - 她很有头脑的{\r}\NWon the debate against theEast Richmond HighSchool. She's got brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是认真的 不必给我任何东西{\r}\NI meant it. Please don't give me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.80,0:23:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 为什么? - 我不知道怎么解释{\r}\N- Nothing? - Oh, I can't explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.47,0:23:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你来了之后 妈妈很开心...{\r}\NBut you came here and Mother's so happy and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢我很高兴我们名字一样{\r}\NOh, I'm glad that she named me after you and that she thinks we're both alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.98,0:23:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想我们是相同的{\r}\NI think we are, too. I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.77,0:23:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你送我东西的话 会破坏事情的{\r}\NOh, it would spoil things if you should give me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.40,0:24:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你真是个奇怪的女孩 那会破坏什么事呢?{\r}\NYou're a strange girl, Charlie. Why would it spoil things?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.61,0:24:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为我们并不仅 是叔叔和外甥女关系{\r}\NBecause we're not just an uncle and a niece. It's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我了解你 别人了解你不多{\r}\NI know you. I know that you don't tell people a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.25,0:24:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我觉得在你身上有些事情...{\r}\NI don't either. I have a feeling that inside you somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.17,0:24:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有其他任何人知道{\r}\Nthere's something nobody knows about.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.42,0:24:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有人知道?{\r}\NSomething... nobody knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.93,0:24:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是一些很惊奇的事情 我会知道的{\r}\NSomething secret and wonderful and... I'll find it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.68,0:24:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}知道太多并不好啊查莉{\r}\NIt's not good to find out too much, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.64,0:24:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们就像双胞胎 不是吗?{\r}\NBut we're sort of like twins. Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.52,0:24:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们都知道的 - 把手给我查莉{\r}\N- We have to know. - Give me your hand, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.70,0:24:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢你{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.33,0:24:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你不看一眼啊 - 我不需要看了{\r}\N- You didn't even look at it. - I don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.25,0:24:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你送我什么都是一样的{\r}\NNo matter what you gave me, it'd be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.42,0:25:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让我给你看看吧{\r}\NHere. Let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.63,0:25:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是一颗绿宝石 很漂亮的{\r}\NIt's a good emerald. A really good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.35,0:25:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}绿宝石是世上 最美丽的东西{\r}\NGood emeralds are the most beautiful things in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.28,0:25:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你刻了一些字在上面 - 没有啊如果你要我帮你拿去刻{\r}\N- You've had something engraved. - I haven't, but I will if you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.74,0:25:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有的查理叔叔 不过有点模糊{\r}\NYes, you have, Uncle Charlie. It's very faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.37,0:25:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}B.M赠予T.S{\r}\N"T.S. From B.M."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.20,0:25:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}像是人名的缩写啊{\r}\NBut... Why, it must be someone's initials.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.83,0:25:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那么我是给珠宝商骗了{\r}\NWell, I've been rooked. The jeweller rooked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.46,0:25:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 噢没所谓的 - 先还我吧我叫人把字去掉{\r}\N- Oh, it doesn't matter. Really. - Give it back. I'll have it taken off.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.88,0:25:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不我喜欢{\r}\NNo, No. I like it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.38,0:25:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}其他人可能会 很喜欢这个的{\r}\NSomeone else was probably happy with this ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.55,0:25:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢真的很美{\r}\NOh, it's perfect the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.51,0:25:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你端咖啡吧{\r}\NYou bring the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.20,0:26:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在餐桌上唱歌 会嫁一个呆丈夫的{\r}\NSing at the table, you'll marry a crazy husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.58,0:26:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}迷信已被证明 是绝对错误的{\r}\NSuperstitions have been proved 100% wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.67,0:26:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对了我想把一些钱 转来这里{\r}\NYes, I've been thinking of transferring some money out here from the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.25,0:26:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在我有计划前 先存在你们银行里祖{\r}\NI could put it in your bank, Joe, until I found out what's what.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.46,0:26:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想你们银行 可以存钱的吧?{\r}\NUh, I suppose your bank does take money, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.88,0:26:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是我们的一项 赚快钱的业务啊{\r}\NThat's one thing we do. Rake in the dough.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.22,0:26:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但不保证可以拿回来{\r}\NCan't promise to give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.22,0:26:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我明天早上 就去开一个户口{\r}\NWell, I'll go downtown in the morning and open an account.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.27,0:26:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 4万美金应该够了吧? - 那是很大的一笔钱啊{\r}\N- 30 or 40,000 just to start things off? - That's a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.02,0:26:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他不会保留很久的 政府会拿走他的钱{\r}\NHe won't have it long. The government will get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.69,0:26:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 政府只会... - 不要说些反政府的话啊罗杰{\r}\N- The government gets - - Don't talk against the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.98,0:26:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}天啊{\r}\NThe way men do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.45,0:26:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的脑子里总是出现那首曲{\r}\NI can't get that tune out of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.20,0:26:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}可能有人告诉过我 但我忘记了{\r}\NMaybe if somebody tells me what it is, I'll forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.95,0:26:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是一首华尔兹 - 我知道但是哪一首呢?{\r}\N- It's a waltz. - I know it is, but what one?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.96,0:26:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真的很奇怪{\r}\NYou know, it's the funniest thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.00,0:27:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我脑子里总是 出现那首曲...{\r}\NSometimes I get a tune in my head like that
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.42,0:27:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不久我好像听到有人也在哼{\r}\Nand pretty soon, I hear somebody else humming it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.46,0:27:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想那首曲一定 在大脑里传来传去{\r}\NI think tunes jump from head to head.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.84,0:27:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道那是什么吗 查理叔叔?{\r}\NDo you know whatit is, Uncle Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.97,0:27:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不我不知道{\r}\NUh, no. No. I-I-I don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.85,0:27:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让我想想...{\r}\NI remember. Uh... It's on the tip of my tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.64,0:27:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}应该是维克托.贺伯特{\r}\NIt's a waltz and it's Victor Herbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.94,0:27:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 维克托.贺伯特不是华尔兹啊 - 应该是蓝色多瑙河吧{\r}\N- Victor Herbert wasn't a waltz. - It's the Blue Danube Waltz.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.61,0:27:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢是啊{\r}\NOh, yes. Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.74,0:27:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不不是的查理叔叔 我知道了是快乐...{\r}\NNo, it isn't, Uncle Charlie. I know what it is. It's the Merry -
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.33,0:27:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起搞得一团糟{\r}\N- I'm terribly sorry, Emmy. - Nothing to make a fuss about.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.79,0:27:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查理我们洗碗的时候 你去客厅那里...{\r}\NCharles, while we do the dishes, why don't you come in the living room
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.12,0:27:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}坐在沙发上看看报纸吧{\r}\Nand stretch out on the sofa and read the evening paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.67,0:27:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你也帮不了什么{\r}\NYou never were much on helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.67,0:27:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 祖贺博来了 - 安妮罗杰来帮我{\r}\N- Joe, here's Herbert. - Ann, Roger, help me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.42,0:27:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}贺博是祖的朋友 他们是评论家{\r}\NHerbert's a friend of Joe's. They're literary critics.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.18,0:27:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你好啊贺博 吃过晚饭了吗?{\r}\NHello, Herb. Had your supper?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.51,0:27:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 一小时前就吃了 - 是吗?{\r}\N- Had mine an hour ago. - Hour ago, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.02,0:28:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 噢手表 - 是礼物{\r}\N- Oh. A watch. - Yeah, a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.02,0:28:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}贺博这位是我内弟{\r}\NHere, Herb. I'd like you to meet my brother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.69,0:28:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查理这位是贺博 - 你好贺博{\r}\N- Charles, this is Herb Hawkins. - Nice to know you, Mr Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.24,0:28:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 谢谢 - 贺博你母亲还好吗?{\r}\N- Fine, thank you. - How's your mother, Herb?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.65,0:28:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢还在恢复{\r}\N- Oh, uh, just middling. - Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.41,0:28:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不好意思贺博{\r}\N- Excuse me, Herb. - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.37,0:28:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 噢 - 你妈妈的事我很难过{\r}\NThank you. I'm sorry your mother's not better.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.71,0:28:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 谢谢你 - 谢谢{\r}\N- Thank you, dear. There, now. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.92,0:28:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}过一种清闲的生活吧{\r}\NLead a life of luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.55,0:28:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要去看查莉在做什么{\r}\NWell, I must go and see what Charlie ' s doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.30,0:28:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我内弟从东部来 纽约人{\r}\NWife's brother from the East. New York man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.81,0:28:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对孩子们好啊 明白我的意思吗?{\r}\NGood for the children. You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.23,0:28:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在生意上? 他可是一个很出众的人{\r}\NIn business? Well, he takes himself very seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.94,0:28:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你的事怎么了?{\r}\NWell, how's everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.53,0:28:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你看过这本书吗?{\r}\NSay, ha-have you read this one? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.74,0:28:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那个法国人把难题都解决了{\r}\NThat little Frenchman beats them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.74,0:28:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就像福尔摩斯那样{\r}\NYou can talk all you like about Sherlock Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.66,0:28:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那个法国人把难题都解决了{\r}\NThat little Frenchman beats 'em all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.66,0:29:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我看过了 但注射气泡未必可以致命{\r}\NI read it. Air bubbles don't necessarily kill a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.12,0:29:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那些作家想像力太丰富了{\r}\NThose writers from the other side get too fancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.13,0:29:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 谋杀的最好方法就是... - 我知道我知道{\r}\N- The best way to commit a murder- - I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.50,0:29:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}用硬器打击头的后部{\r}\NHit 'em on the head with a blunt instrument.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.76,0:29:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对极了不是吗?听着{\r}\NWell, it's true, isn't it? Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.38,0:29:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果我想明天谋杀你{\r}\NIf I wanted to murder you tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.51,0:29:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我还会浪费时间 去给你做皮下注射吗?{\r}\Ndo you think I'd waste my time on fancy hypodermics?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.60,0:29:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 或者是伊尼? - 那是什么?{\r}\N- Or on Inee? - What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.64,0:29:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}伊尼是一种 印度毒箭上的毒药   哦{\r}\N- Inee. Indian arrow poison. - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.56,0:29:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果我发现你一个人走着{\r}\NListen, I'd find out if you were alone, walk in,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.98,0:29:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我就用铁管给你的头几下{\r}\Nhit you on the head with a piece of lead pipe or a loaded cane -
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.28,0:29:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那有什么意思?{\r}\NWhat'd be the fun of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.36,0:29:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你的计划呢? 你的线索呢?{\r}\NWhere's your planning? Where's your clues?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.12,0:29:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不想有什么线索 我只想谋杀你{\r}\NI don't want any clues. I want to murder you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.78,0:29:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要线索来做什么?{\r}\NWhat do I want with clues?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.16,0:29:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果没有线索那怎么成书?{\r}\NWell, if you haven't got any clues, where's your book?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.29,0:29:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不是在说写书 我说的是要谋杀你!{\r}\NI'm not talkin' 'bout writing books. I'm talking about killing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.00,0:29:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果我要谋杀你的话 我才不会用那些笨重的工具{\r}\NIf I was going to kill you, I wouldn't do a dumb thing like hitting you on the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.13,0:29:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}首先 我不想被人找到指纹{\r}\NFirst of all, I don't like the fingerprint angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.68,0:29:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会戴手套 将你的手按在那铁管上...{\r}\NOf course, I could always wear gloves, press your hands against the pipe
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.85,0:30:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}造成是你自杀的情形,噢!{\r}\Nafter you were dead and make you look like a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.98,0:30:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但那是很难让人相信你是自杀的 所以我要谋杀你而不被看出是谋杀{\r}\NBut you wouldn't beat yourself to death. I'd do it so it didn't look like murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.30,0:30:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 安妮?{\r}\NOh, Ann?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.34,0:30:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 什么? - 来这里{\r}\N- What? - Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.85,0:30:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你见过怎样用报纸 做一间房子吗?{\r}\NDid you ever see a house made out of newspapers?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.18,0:30:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看好了{\r}\NWell, watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.56,0:30:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}先拿一张报纸出来{\r}\NYou-You take one sheet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.52,0:30:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}然后在这里撕开{\r}\NOK? And you tear it down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.78,0:30:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那里也撕开{\r}\NAnd you tear it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.53,0:30:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}然后从两边折起来{\r}\NYou fold it over here at the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.53,0:31:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}叠在一起{\r}\NFold over the other side here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.66,0:31:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这样竖起来{\r}\NAnd turn it up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.04,0:31:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}然后门口...{\r}\NNow with... the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.71,0:31:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就是这里了{\r}\NRight off... and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.58,0:31:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我已经不是小孩了 而且这是爸爸的报纸{\r}\NI'm not a baby any more. Besides, that's Papa's paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.67,0:31:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}罗杰看看这是什么 一间可爱的小棚子{\r}\NOh, Roger, look what we ' ve got. A nice, little red barn.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.59,0:31:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那是爸爸的报纸啊 - 没什么的{\r}\N- You've got Papa's paper. - Oh, that's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.72,0:31:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再摊开就没事了 - 没人会看出来的{\r}\NSimply unfold it. Nobody will ever know the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.93,0:31:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你们在做什么?{\r}\NWhat are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.89,0:31:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你们都知道那是爸爸的报纸 - 噢查莉是我的错, 我在玩个小游戏{\r}\N- You know that's father's paper. - It's my fault. I was playing a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.73,0:31:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不知道那是你爸爸的报纸 - 噢没什么{\r}\N- Didn't think about it as Joe's pap. - Oh, that's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.36,0:31:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}第一页第五页 第八页...{\r}\NHere's page one, five... eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.28,0:31:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 第三和第四页在哪里? - 我们没碰过啊{\r}\N- What did you do with three and four? - We never touched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.08,0:31:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只有查理叔叔碰过{\r}\NReally. Uncle Charlie ' s the only one that touched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.25,0:31:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}应该没什么的{\r}\NOh, well. I guess it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.91,0:31:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}放整齐一点 爸爸可能看不出来{\r}\NIf I fold it very neatly, maybe he won ' t notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.59,0:32:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请进{\r}\NCome in.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.18,0:32:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我给你拿了些水{\r}\NI brought you water.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.43,0:32:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 谢谢你{\r}\NOh, thank you, Charlie. That's very thoughtful of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.06,0:32:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}祝你好梦{\r}\NPleasant dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.48,0:32:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查理叔叔{\r}\NUncle Charlie...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.02,0:32:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道了一些你以为我不知道的秘密 什么秘密?{\r}\N- I know a secret you don't think I know. - What secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.78,0:32:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}记得我说过不要隐藏什么 因为我会发现的吗?{\r}\NRemember I said you couldn't hide anything from me because I'd find it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.95,0:32:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在我知道今晚的报纸 和你是有关系的{\r}\NWell, now I know there was something in the evening paper about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.12,0:32:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 和我有关? - 是的{\r}\NAbout me in the evening paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.16,0:32:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所以你才和 安妮和罗杰玩那游戏{\r}\NAnd that's why you played that game with Ann and Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.75,0:32:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不想我们知道 并把报纸撕掉了{\r}\NYou didn't want us to know and you wanted to tear the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.92,0:32:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想你应该告诉我吧{\r}\NNow I know. You might as well tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.75,0:32:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}被你捉到了查莉{\r}\NWell, you've got me there, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.47,0:32:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}并不完全和我有关只是...{\r}\NOnly it wasn't about me. It was about, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.47,0:32:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我以前认识的某人{\r}\Nsomeone I used to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.31,0:32:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看看!{\r}\NThere!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.85,0:32:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那不关你的事!{\r}\NIt's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.39,0:32:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢查理叔叔 你弄痛我了{\r}\NOh! Uncle Charlie, you're hurting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.27,0:32:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢查莉你的手{\r}\N- Oh, Charlie. - Your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.82,0:33:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉我无意弄痛你的{\r}\NCharlie, I didn't mean to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.32,0:33:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是玩着的{\r}\NI was just fooling.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.49,0:33:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那只是...一些流言{\r}\NIt was nothing. Just... Just some gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.41,0:33:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是我以前的朋友的绯闻{\r}\NNot very pretty, about someone I once met up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.25,0:33:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不适合你们看的{\r}\NNot for you to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.76,0:33:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}忘记它吧{\r}\NForget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.34,0:33:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 晚安小查莉 - 晚安查理叔叔好梦{\r}\N- Good night, young Charlie. - Good night. Pleasant dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.61,0:33:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查理叔叔会逗留多久? - 他不走就好了{\r}\N- How long is Uncle Charlie staying? - Forever, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.87,0:33:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他自己没有屋子吗?{\r}\NHasn't he got a house of his own?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.87,0:33:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}既然你现在来这里了 我希望...{\r}\NNot that I mind you in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.08,0:33:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}可以保留一点隐私{\r}\Nbut I never can tell when I'll want some privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.83,0:33:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你还是睡觉吧小宝贝{\r}\NYou better go to sleep, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.50,0:33:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 祈祷了吗? - 我忘记了{\r}\N- You said your prayers? - I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.59,0:34:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还是祈祷吧{\r}\NYou better say them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.13,0:34:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我即将睡觉 希望上帝...{\r}\NI lay me down to sleep, I pray the Lord my soul to keep -
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.68,0:34:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 别说太说很晚了 - 带走我的心灵{\r}\N- Don't bless too many people. It's late. - I pray the Lord my soul to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.72,0:34:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}愿上帝保佑我妈妈爸爸 还有总统...{\r}\NGod bless Mama, Papa, Captain Midnight, Veronica Lake and the president -
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.77,0:34:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 亲爱的你这样说没完没了啊 - 还有查理叔叔阿门{\r}\N- You can't say them all tonight, dear. - Oh, and Uncle Charlie. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.26,0:34:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 准备好吃早餐了吗? - 噢是咖啡啊艾玛{\r}\N- All ready for breakfast? - Oh, coffee, Emmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.06,0:34:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道你怎么会 喜欢在床上吃东西{\r}\NI don't know how you do it. Now, I'm never comfortable eating in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.64,0:34:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}孩子们回来之后 我有时也会在床上吃...{\r}\NI had to have my meals in bed for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.98,0:35:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我不喜欢那样{\r}\Nafter the children came, but I never liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.94,0:35:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}早上我不知道该做什么好 说话前也要先喝一杯咖啡{\r}\NI can't face the world in the morning. I must have coffee before I can speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.36,0:35:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不介意纵容你一下{\r}\NWell, I don't mind pampering you your first morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.11,0:35:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我想你在镇是唯一 在十点半吃早餐的人了{\r}\Nbut I think you're the only person in this town to have breakfast at 10:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.12,0:35:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你还在睡的时候 报社的人说想来做个访问{\r}\NAnd while you were sleeping, the newspaper called up for an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.29,0:35:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}访问我?{\r}\NWith me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.83,0:35:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我参加的那个妇女 俱乐部希望你去做一次演讲{\r}\NAnd the women's club I belong to wants you to give a little talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.63,0:35:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妇女俱乐部{\r}\NWomen's club.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.63,0:35:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢你还没把东西放好啊 我帮你吧{\r}\NOh! Oh, you haven't finished unpacking. I'll do that for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.13,0:35:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查莉去哪里了? - 她在屋子里团团转像傻了一样{\r}\N- Where ' s Charlie? - She's running around like a mad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.14,0:35:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她觉得什么都需要修理一下{\r}\NShe thinks everything needs fixing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.14,0:35:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我告诉你 你可不是这里唯一的名人{\r}\NBut what I wanted to tell you was that you're not the only celebrity in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.14,0:35:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}牛顿一家都成为了镇里的 关注焦点你想说什么?{\r}\N- We're all going to be in limelight. - What are you cooking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.52,0:35:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今天早上来的那个 叫格翰的年轻人...{\r}\NWell, a young man called this morning, said his name was Graham,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.98,0:35:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}想采访我们家里的{\r}\Nand he wants to interview everybody in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.15,0:35:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 采访所有人? - 他是那样说的{\r}\N- Interview everybody? - That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.41,0:35:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他说是什么委员会派他来...{\r}\NHe's being sent around the country by some kind of institute or committee
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.41,0:35:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}挑选有代表性的 美国家庭来访问{\r}\Nand he has to pick a representative American family and ask them questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.33,0:36:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}像是一种调查 国家公众调查{\r}\NIt's a kind of a poll. It's called the National Public Survey.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.79,0:36:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为什么他要选这个家庭呢?{\r}\NWonder how he happened to pick this family?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.84,0:36:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他说要挑选有 代表性的美国家庭{\r}\NWell, he said he wanted a typical American family.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.55,0:36:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我告诉他我们不是的{\r}\NI told him we weren't a typical American family.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.30,0:36:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果他们问我的事情 我就不会回答他们{\r}\NIf he's going to ask a lot of questions, he can leave me out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.97,0:36:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢你的事情 我们也说不详细啊{\r}\NOh, but you could tell him so much more than any of us could.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.81,0:36:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他说还要拍照片 - 拍照片{\r}\N- He's going to take our pictures too. - Pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.35,0:36:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢多么漂亮啊{\r}\NMy, isn't that lovely?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.52,0:36:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们两个都是很年轻的{\r}\NYou see, there were really, there were two young men.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.65,0:36:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一个负责拍照{\r}\NOne of them takes the pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.36,0:36:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 噢还有两个人啊 - 是的格翰先生为人好一点{\r}\N- Oh, there were two. - Yes. Mr Graham was the nicest.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.78,0:36:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他说我们不必打扮的{\r}\NOh, he doesn't want us to dress up or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.20,0:36:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他就想我们像往常一样{\r}\NHe just wants us to act the way we always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.79,0:36:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 艾玛女人都是很笨的 - 她们总会坏事{\r}\NEmmy, women are fools. They'd fall for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.88,0:36:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为什么你会让 两个陌生人进屋里捣乱?{\r}\NWhy do you let two strangers come and turn this place upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.55,0:36:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哪个家庭会欢迎 那些窥探者呢?{\r}\NWhy expose the family to a couple of snoopers?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.51,0:36:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你应该警觉一点 - 查理我只是...{\r}\N- You should have more sense. - Why, Charles, I -
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.89,0:36:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 早安查理叔叔 - 早安查莉{\r}\N- Good morning, Uncle Charlie. - Good morning, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.72,0:37:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你妈妈说牛顿家 被一些小毛孩选中了{\r}\NYour mother says the Newtons have been picked for all-American suckers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.23,0:37:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你怎么认为? - 他们来的时候查莉不在{\r}\N- What do you know about it? - Charlie wasn't here when they came.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.52,0:37:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是格翰先生的行为... 一点也不像是窥探{\r}\NBut really, the way Mr Graham told it, it wasn't like snooping at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.65,0:37:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是公民的责任 是政府的需要{\r}\NIt was our duty as citizens. It's something the government wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.40,0:37:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}政府?可能不太准确 但那是为了公众利益{\r}\N- Government? - Well, it's for the public good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.41,0:37:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当我告诉他们你曾去过 哪些地方时他们很感兴趣{\r}\NI told them about you andtheplaces you've been and he was very interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.33,0:37:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}艾玛我与此事是无关的{\r}\NNow, listen, Emmy. I'll have nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.87,0:37:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我只是来探望你们 我建议你请他们吃闭门羹吧{\r}\NI'm just a visitor here and my advice to you is to slam the door in his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.21,0:37:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢我不能这样做啊{\r}\NOh. Well, I-I couldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.67,0:37:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你不想的话 可以不见他们的{\r}\NBut you don't have to meet him if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.84,0:37:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我觉得那很有意思啊{\r}\NWell, I think I'd be kind of exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.84,0:37:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他拿你的照片 也没什么作用啊{\r}\NHe'd take your photograph and then we could have it for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.38,0:37:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不了我这一生都没拍过照 我也不想拍照{\r}\NNo thank you. I've never been photographed and I don't want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.22,0:37:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢查理 你怎么可以这样说呢?{\r}\NOh, Charles, how can you talk that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.22,0:37:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我有你的照片 给查莉保管着{\r}\NI had a photograph of you. I gave it to Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.18,0:37:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我说过没有啊 - 我想你忘记了{\r}\NI tell you, there are none. I guess you've forgotten this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.94,0:37:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}去拿吧查莉{\r}\NGet it, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.44,0:37:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你真的记不起来吗?{\r}\NYou sure you don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.44,0:37:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}被人拍下来的我 当然记不起来{\r}\NOf course I don't ever remember being photographed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.62,0:37:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}本翰大街46号{\r}\N46 Burnham Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.78,0:38:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那自行车是你的圣诞礼物{\r}\NMm-hm. It was taken the Christmas you got your bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.20,0:38:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那时就在你出意外之前 - 查理叔叔你很可爱啊{\r}\N- Just before your accident. - Uncle Charlie, you were beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.79,0:38:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是吧?他那时很文静 喜欢读书{\r}\NWasn't he, though? And such a quiet boy. Always reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.88,0:38:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}爸爸不应该给你买那自行车的 你不懂怎么骑{\r}\NPapa shouldn't have got you that bicycle. You didn't know how to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.22,0:38:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他在冰滑的路上骑车 并撞到了电车{\r}\NHe took it right out on the icy road and skidded into a streetcar.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.97,0:38:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们以为他不行了 幸好他没事{\r}\N- We thought he was going to die. - I'm glad he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.14,0:38:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那真的很险头骨也裂了 躺了很久{\r}\NHe almost did. He fractured his skull, and he was laid up so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.10,0:38:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}然后他慢慢康复了{\r}\NAnd then, when he was getting well, there was no holding him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.94,0:38:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}之后的事情对他来说 似乎太不足够了...{\r}\NAnd it was just as though all the rest he had was too much for him
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.32,0:38:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他开始变得淘气起来{\r}\Nand he had to get into mischief to blow off steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.32,0:38:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那事之后 他再也没怎么读书了{\r}\NHe didn't do much reading after that, let me tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.41,0:38:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他在意外养伤的时候 就已经读够了{\r}\NIt was taken the very day he had his accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.16,0:38:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不久之后这张照片拿了回家 妈妈哭得很厉害{\r}\NA few days later when the pictures came home, how mama cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.75,0:38:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}担心他的样子 和为人会不会变了{\r}\NShe wondered if he'd ever look the same. She wondered if he'd ever be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.34,0:38:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}回顾过去有什么用? 展望未来又有什么用?{\r}\NWhat's the use of looking backward? What's the use of looking ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.80,0:38:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今天才是关键 那就是我的哲学今天{\r}\NToday's the thing. That's my philosophy. Today.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.18,0:39:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果这样那你就 应该快点把早餐吃完...{\r}\NIf today's the thing, then you'd better finish your breakfast
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.14,0:39:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}然后赶快去银行 祖在等你呢{\r}\Nand get down to the bank because Joe'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.27,0:39:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉你不要迟到啊 做调查的人四点就来了{\r}\NCharlie, don't be late back. The survey men are coming at 4:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.03,0:39:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你好查莉 - 你好梅芝{\r}\N- Good morning, Charlie. - Hello, Madge.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.03,0:39:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你好查莉 - 你好卡芙琳{\r}\N- Good morning, Charlie. - Hello, Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.55,0:39:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看到她们怎么看你的吗? 一定很想知道你是谁{\r}\NDid you see the way they looked at you? I bet they wonder who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.63,0:39:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢查理叔叔我想和你说话 大家都在看着我{\r}\NUncle Charlie, I love to walk with you. I want everybody to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.99,0:40:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}爸爸就在那个窗口{\r}\NThere's Papa in that window over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.46,0:40:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}祖挪用公款的事 晚些再忙好吗?{\r}\NHello, Joe. Can you stop embezzling a minute and give me your attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.63,0:40:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢...{\r}\NOh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.46,0:40:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查理我们在这里 不开那种玩笑的{\r}\NCharles, we don't joke about such things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.67,0:40:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢那在月底总数的 不足是什么?{\r}\NOh, what's a little shortage in the books at the end of the month?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.26,0:40:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一个好的银行职员 知道该怎么做的对吗查莉?{\r}\NAny good bank clerk can cover up alittle shortage. Isn't that right, Charlie
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.10,0:40:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 大家都听到了 - 那就好大家都知道这里是银行{\r}\N- Everyone can hear you. - Good. We all know what banks are.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.18,0:40:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看上去很正常但在内里 就不知道有什么发生了{\r}\NLook all right, but noone knows what goes on when they lock the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.02,0:40:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但骗不了我祖 带我去见你们的经理吧{\r}\NCan't fool me, though. Well, Joe, let's see your president.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.86,0:40:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你还要开个户口吗查理? - 我就为此而来啊{\r}\NStill want to open that account, Charles? That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.24,0:40:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那你在这里先等一下 我去找格林先生{\r}\NWell, uh, you wait right here. I'll see if Mr Greene's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.70,0:40:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查理他不喜欢 开那种玩笑的{\r}\NAnd, uh, Charles, he doesn't care much for jokes about banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.08,0:40:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想四万美金对他来说 肯定不是玩笑了吧{\r}\NWell, $40,000 is no joke. Not to him, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.91,0:40:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是我的一个玩笑 这个世界都在拿我开玩笑{\r}\NIt's a joke to me. The whole world's a joke to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.63,0:40:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我很快回来{\r}\NI'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.80,0:41:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不应该那样逗我爸爸{\r}\NYou shouldn't tease Papa like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.97,0:41:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不是要逗他 我只是不喜欢这里的气氛{\r}\NI wasn't teasing him. I just hate this stuffy atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.89,0:41:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他叫我们进去啊{\r}\NThey're waving for us to come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.40,0:41:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你好格林先生 - 你好查莉{\r}\N- Hello, Mr Greene. - Hello, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.49,0:41:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}格林先生这位是我内弟 奥克里先生{\r}\NWell, Mr Greene, this is my brother-in-law, Mr Oakley.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.82,0:41:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你好 - 你好奥克里先生{\r}\N- How do you do? - How are you, Mr Oakley?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.82,0:41:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}格林先生我打算 在这里逗留一段时间{\r}\NWell, Mr Greene, I was thinking of settling down here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.24,0:41:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 强大的国家{\r}\NGreat country. Great country.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.04,0:41:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 当然你最近在干什么?{\r}\NWe think so. What have you been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.54,0:41:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为这里做点贡献{\r}\NI suppose you might call me a promoter. I've done a little bit of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.42,0:41:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}问题是当我赚到钱 我就对钱没有了兴趣{\r}\NThe only trouble is that once I make the money, I'm not interested in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.21,0:41:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对钱没有了兴趣?{\r}\NNot interested in money?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.97,0:41:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}外面有很多钱 在等着有人去捡啊{\r}\NYou know there's money just lying around waiting for somebody to pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.80,0:41:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想我应该 把一些零钱存起来{\r}\NI thought maybe I'd put some of my loose cash away for safekeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.01,0:41:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很自然我就想到了祖工作的 银行零钱?{\r}\N- In the bank where Joe works, naturally. - Loose cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.68,0:41:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我有个习惯在旅行的时候 带着大量的现金{\r}\NWell, I got in a habit of carrying a lot of cash with me when I was travelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.65,0:41:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是个危险的习惯啊奥克里先生 - 我还没丢过一分钱呢格林先生{\r}\N- A dangerous habit. - Never lost a penny in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.86,0:42:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想上天是 保佑那些蠢人和恶棍的{\r}\NI guess heaven takes care of fools and scoundrels.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.44,0:42:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是啊 - 三万三万五四万{\r}\N- Yes. - Thirty, thirty-five...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.32,0:42:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}四万开个户口好吗?{\r}\NForty thousand. Shall we start with forty?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.37,0:42:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只要填一张资料纸就可以了 奥克里先生细节的问题{\r}\N- If you'll just write out a deposit slip. - Ah, details.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.50,0:42:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你遇到我这样注意 细节的人就对了格林先生{\r}\NI'm glad to see you're a man who understands details, Mr Greene.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.25,0:42:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那些对我是最重要的 每个细节都很重要{\r}\NThey're most important to me. Most important. All the little details.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.84,0:42:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢不好意思 不知道你们在忙{\r}\NOh, dear. I'm sorry. I didn't know you were busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.55,0:42:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们迟点来吧 - 进来吧既然已经来了{\r}\N- We can come back. - Come in, now that you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.39,0:42:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}格林太太这位是我叔叔 奥克里先生{\r}\NMrs Greene, I'd like you to meet my uncle, Mr Oakley.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.81,0:42:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查理叔叔这两位是 格林太太和波特太太{\r}\NUncle Charlie, this is Mrs Greene and Mrs Potter.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.56,0:42:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}格林太太波特小姐{\r}\NMrs Greene, Miss Potter.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.02,0:42:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是波特太太{\r}\NMrs Potter.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.44,0:42:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我可不那么认为 - 是吗?{\r}\N- Something about you made me think - - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.15,0:42:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 怎么了玛格莉? - 我们想购物但现在只有五块钱{\r}\N- What did you want, Margaret? - I need some money to go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.62,0:42:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}做寡妇也有一点是好的{\r}\NThere's one good thing in being a widow, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.62,0:42:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就是不用问丈夫要钱花{\r}\NYou don't have to ask your husband for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.41,0:42:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 给你 - 噢谢谢{\r}\N- Here you are. - Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.96,0:43:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再见奥克里先生 波特太太{\r}\N- Goodbye, Mr Oakley. - Mrs Potter.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.21,0:43:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再见格林太太{\r}\NBye, Mrs Greene.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.51,0:43:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好了格林先生{\r}\NThere. There you are, Mr Greene.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.63,0:43:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查莉我们去吃午饭吧 - 再见奥克里先生{\r}\N- Charlie, let's see the town. - Goodbye, Mr Oakley.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.35,0:43:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 再见格林先生 - 有问题随时可以来查询{\r}\N- Bye, Mr Greene. - Call on us for advice anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.43,0:43:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 谢谢 - 祖送奥克里先生出门吧{\r}\N- Thank you. - Joe, you may see Mr Oakley out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.39,0:43:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}祖只要你醒目点 他的位置迟早是你的{\r}\NJoe, keep your eyes open. You'll have his job in a couple of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.95,0:43:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他回来了{\r}\NHere he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.59,0:43:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那些做调查的人来了 早了一个小时啊{\r}\NThose must be the questionnaire men. They're a whole hour early.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.80,0:43:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不会见他们的 - 别担心{\r}\NI won't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.84,0:43:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不想的话就不见吧 我明白的{\r}\NYou don't have to if you don't want to. I'll see that you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.35,0:43:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}小心他们对你母亲做什么{\r}\NThe way they got around your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.39,0:43:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想她要警惕一点{\r}\NI thought she'd have better sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.61,0:44:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你好 - 你好{\r}\N- How do you do? - How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.40,0:44:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你们应该就是来做调查的吧 - 我是格翰牛顿太太{\r}\N- You must have come to interview us. - My name is Graham, Miss Newton.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.53,0:44:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你好 - 这位是桑德斯{\r}\N- Oh, how do you do? - And this is Fred Saunders.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.82,0:44:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你好   请进来{\r}\NHow do you do? Won't you come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.16,0:44:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我去叫妈妈 - 谢谢{\r}\N- I'll call my mother. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.66,0:44:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈妈他们进来了{\r}\NMother, the government men are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.83,0:44:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请做{\r}\NWill you sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.83,0:44:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们说是四点的 现在还没准备好啊{\r}\NBut you said 4:00. Nothing's ready now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.21,0:44:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我丈夫还在银行 而这里...{\r}\NMy husband is still at the bank and-and the house is -
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.55,0:44:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们就是想这样 牛顿太太{\r}\NThat's all we want now, Mrs Newton, some pictures of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.13,0:44:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}桑德斯会在周围拍照 而我就问你问题{\r}\NSaunders can get busy and I'd like to ask a few questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.18,0:44:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好的但我希望你们 等我把房子收拾好了{\r}\NAlright, but I do wish you'd waited until I had the house looking its best.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.93,0:44:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想在这里安放鲜花 还有在厨房里挂新的窗窗布{\r}\NI wanted flowers around and fresh curtains in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.14,0:44:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还有很多东西我想你们拍照的{\r}\NAnd there are a lot of things I don't want you to photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.73,0:44:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你们拥有这房子吗? - 不是房子拥有我们{\r}\N- You said you own the house? - Own it? It owns us.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.57,0:44:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有一样东西开始要修理的话 整间房子都要修理了{\r}\NNo sooner do I get one thing fixed than something else gets broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.36,0:44:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}要再刷一下油漆...{\r}\NAnd then it needs fresh paint and th-
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.70,0:44:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}桑德斯先生 不好意思...{\r}\NMr Saunders, I'm very sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.70,0:44:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请不要给这张椅子拍照{\r}\Nbut you simply cannot take a picture with that chair in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.95,0:45:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 要套一个沙发套 - 你们家有六个人?{\r}\N- It needs a new slipcover. - And there are, uh, six in your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.75,0:45:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是五个 - 五个?但是...{\r}\N- Five. - Five? But -
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.38,0:45:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我叔叔只是来探望我们的{\r}\NWell, my uncle ' s just visiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.42,0:45:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我说过他的 他是从东部来的{\r}\NI told you about him. He's here from the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.46,0:45:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我叔叔不希望有什么麻烦{\r}\NMy uncle doesn't want to be bothered with a lot of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.80,0:45:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}做调查的时候我们要...{\r}\NWell, you see, on a survey, we usually -
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.14,0:45:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他对调查不感兴趣...{\r}\NHe's not interested in a survey
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.14,0:45:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我答应过他不会骚扰他的{\r}\Nand I promised him he wouldn ' t be bothered.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.60,0:45:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们希望你们都参与{\r}\NWell, we'd like it if we could get all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.60,0:45:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}想了解你们做什么 和想做些什么{\r}\NYou know, your opinions, what you do or what you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.98,0:45:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我叔叔的意见很特别的 我想你们不会接受{\r}\NMy uncle's opinions aren't average and I'm afraid they wouldn't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.36,0:45:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想每个人都有自己的思想{\r}\NI think when someone asks for privacy, they should have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.90,0:45:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}其实我们这次的目的是...{\r}\NWell, we'll... The whole idea of this thing is that -
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.07,0:45:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}格翰先生我想你们应该 选择另外的家庭{\r}\NMr Graham, perhaps you'd better choose another family.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.66,0:45:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们也有这样做的 但你们的家庭是...{\r}\NWe'll do anything you say, of course, but this family seemed right and -
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.33,0:45:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是一个很好的家庭{\r}\NIt is a nice family.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.33,0:45:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉你为什么 不让他问下去呢?{\r}\NCharlie, let the young men go ahead, so long as they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.38,0:45:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那好吧{\r}\NWell, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.84,0:45:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好的桑德斯 去拍些照片吧{\r}\NOK. Saunders, go ahead and get another shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.84,0:45:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}牛顿太太可以告诉 我你丈夫在哪里工作吗?{\r}\NMrs Newton, what organisations do you and your husband belong to?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.05,0:45:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在厨房照一张好吗?{\r}\NHow about a picture in the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.05,0:45:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想不是很适合{\r}\NWell, I'm afraid the kitchen isn't quite the way I'd like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.43,0:46:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}过来{\r}\NCome along.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.98,0:46:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}牛顿太太 你要先打鸡蛋吧{\r}\NIf you'll start by breakin' an egg, Mrs Newton.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.44,0:46:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢不不应该先打蛋的{\r}\NOh, but you don't start a cake by breaking an egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.36,0:46:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}要先把牛油和糖放进去{\r}\NYou have to put the butter and sugar in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.65,0:46:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有没有调查 我都不会先打蛋的{\r}\NSurvey or no survey, I'm not going to start by breaking an egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.78,0:46:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要做一个枫叶蛋糕 我弟弟很爱吃的{\r}\NI thought I'd make a maple cake. My brother Charles loves maple cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.66,0:46:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你弟弟做什么的? - 我想他什么都做{\r}\NWhat does your brother do? I guess he just does about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.04,0:46:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是什么工作? - 应该是做生意的男人都是那样{\r}\NWhat does he do? He's just in business. You know, the way men are.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.04,0:46:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我丈夫在银行 但我想查理是生意人{\r}\NMy husband works in a bank, but I think Charles is just in business.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.80,0:46:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你要在 我打蛋的时候拍照{\r}\NIf you really want a picture of me breaking an egg,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.30,0:46:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那就要等我把 牛油和糖放进去{\r}\Nyou'll have to wait till I cream the butter and sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.31,0:46:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会等的{\r}\NI'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.31,0:46:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我可以到楼上看看吗?{\r}\NI wonder if we could take a look upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.48,0:46:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请你带我去吧 你妈妈会叫我的好的{\r}\NYou show us, and your mother can call us when she's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.48,0:46:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}桑德斯先生{\r}\N- Alright. - If you'd rather wait, Mr Saunders.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.61,0:46:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}加蛋的时间要很及时{\r}\NFolding in the eggs has to be done just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.48,0:46:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不能让它等得太久{\r}\NI can ' t beat them and let them stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.49,0:46:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我一听到你打蛋的声音 就马上下来{\r}\NThe minute I hear you've broken the eggs, I'll come right down.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.99,0:46:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好的{\r}\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.83,0:47:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道你想找什么{\r}\NI really don't see what you want to look up here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.71,0:47:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那间房是谁的?本来 是我的现在查理叔叔住着{\r}\NWhose room is that? It's mine. My uncle's using it now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.21,0:47:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想知道 里面的布局是怎样的{\r}\NI'd like to see what your room looks like. Typical girl, typical room.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.09,0:47:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我叔叔正在休息{\r}\NTypical of you to ask. My uncle's resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.80,0:47:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不想打扰他{\r}\NI really don't want to disturb him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.10,0:47:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那是后楼梯吗? - 没错可以到大厅的{\r}\N- Is there a back stairs? - Mm-hm. Right down the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.64,0:47:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我和你打赌 你叔叔不在里面{\r}\NI'll bet you 50 cents that your uncle isn't in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.39,0:47:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}打赌很无聊的{\r}\NOh, betting's silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.40,0:47:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你只是想进去拍照{\r}\NAll you want to do is photograph my room, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.36,0:47:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道叔叔在里面{\r}\N- That's it. - Besides, I know my uncle's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.44,0:47:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我还是认为他在里面 我们进去看看吧{\r}\NAlright, I'll still bet he isn't. Let me knock and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.16,0:47:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我先敲门{\r}\NOh, I'll knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.87,0:47:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查理叔叔?{\r}\NUncle Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.66,0:47:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查理叔叔 我们可以进来吗?{\r}\NUncle Charlie, may we come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.67,0:47:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 看到了吗? - 你说得对{\r}\N- See? - You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.42,0:47:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不错的房间啊 可以拍几张照片吗?{\r}\NNice room. Do you mind if I take a picture since he isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.34,0:48:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我真的不想打扰你叔叔 - 我知道{\r}\N- I don't want to disturb your uncle. - Oh, I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.39,0:48:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我想不到 谁会对我的房间感兴趣{\r}\NBut I really can't imagine anyone being interested in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.18,0:48:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我喜欢现在的颜色 我喜欢全部是白色{\r}\NIt's not the way I'd like it. I'd like to have it yellow and white.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.14,0:48:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他想享受宁静啊{\r}\NMight as well let him work in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.15,0:48:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想和他说几句{\r}\NBesides, I'd like to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.94,0:48:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说我们是普通家庭 但我觉得很有意思{\r}\NYour picking us as an average family gave me a funny feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.99,0:48:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 什么有意思? - 我不知道{\r}\N- What kind of a funny feeling? - Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.03,0:48:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想是我不想 做一个普通女孩吧{\r}\NI guess I don't like to be and average girl in an average family.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.95,0:48:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}普通家庭才是好的 看看我{\r}\NAverage families are the best. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.08,0:48:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我也是来自普通家庭的 - 和我们一样普通?{\r}\N- I'm from an average family. - As average as ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.58,0:48:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然是了 但我还不确定你们很普通{\r}\NSure. Besides, I don't think you're average.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.96,0:48:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是因为你们现在来这里 而不是前几天{\r}\NOh, that's because you see me now instead of a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.46,0:48:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我那时很灰暗 查理叔叔来了就改变了{\r}\NI was in the dumps. Then Uncle Charlie came and everything changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.93,0:48:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但你妈妈说他昨晚才到的 可能你...{\r}\NBut your mother said he came last night. Maybe you just think -
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.02,0:48:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道的{\r}\NI don't think. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.93,0:48:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很有趣每次我想东西的时候 总会想到查理叔叔{\r}\NFunny, but when I think about how I feel, I always come back to Uncle Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.32,0:48:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而你不想让我 觉得他很不简单吗?{\r}\NAre you trying to tell me I shouldn't think he's so wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.11,0:49:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 噢我只是... - 桑德斯先生?{\r}\N- Oh, no. I - - Mr Saunders?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.28,0:49:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我准备好打蛋了希望 桑德斯先生不会搞得很乱{\r}\N- I'm ready with the eggs. - Mr Saunders mustn't move anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.12,0:49:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我叔叔是很整洁和挑剔的 - 桑德斯先生也是的{\r}\N- My uncle's awfully neat and fussy. - Saunders is neat and fussy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.79,0:49:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这是你提起的叔叔吗? - 是的{\r}\N- Is this your uncle? - Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.34,0:49:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在来一张走廊的{\r}\NNow, for one of the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.89,0:49:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}桑德斯先生在 我房间拍了几张照片{\r}\NMr Saunders has been taking pictures of my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.35,0:49:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我姐姐提醒你们 那些鸡蛋和蛋糕{\r}\NMy sister told me to remind you about eggs and a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.73,0:49:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不想被拍照 我要拿回那底片{\r}\NI don't like to be photographed. I'll have to ask you for the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.98,0:49:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 噢查理叔叔 - 请给我{\r}\N- Oh, Uncle Charlie. - Give it to me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.32,0:49:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}给他吧桑德斯{\r}\NGive it to him, Fred.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.99,0:49:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真可惜牛顿太太 的照片也在里面{\r}\NThat's too bad. There's a picture of Mrs Newton on this film.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.00,0:49:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不好意思桑德斯先生 我准备好加蛋了{\r}\N- Excuse me. - The eggs are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.17,0:50:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不能再让它等着了{\r}\NI can't let them stand another minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.39,0:50:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那是最后一卷胶卷了 - 噢{\r}\NThat was my last roll of film.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.68,0:50:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}桑德斯先生 给查理叔叔拍照...{\r}\NMr Saunders took Uncle Charlie's picture by mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.18,0:50:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查理叔叔把胶卷拿了{\r}\Nand Uncle Charlie made him give him back the roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.02,0:50:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他不是在开玩笑的{\r}\NHe wasn't joking about not wanting to be photographed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.85,0:50:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们都不想 有什么家庭纠纷{\r}\NWe didn't want to start a family feud.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.86,0:50:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们明天再来 看你做蛋糕吧{\r}\NI'll get you making the cake again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.86,0:50:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我明天不会做蛋糕了{\r}\NI won't be making a cake again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.40,0:50:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要做一些 很重要的事情{\r}\NI want to help an important work, but I cannot go on making cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.07,0:50:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你已经帮我们了 牛顿太太{\r}\NYou have helped, Mrs Newton.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.12,0:50:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我还想问一下{\r}\NAnd now I'd like to ask another favour.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.12,0:50:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今天晚上可以约你的女儿 出去吗?我想四处看看{\r}\NCould I borrow your daughter? I'd like to look around the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.54,0:50:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 安妮? - 是查莉{\r}\N- Ann? - Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.54,0:50:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安妮会好些 她什么都知道{\r}\NAnn would be better. Ann knows everything about everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.71,0:50:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查莉 - 如果查莉不介意的话{\r}\N- Charlie. - Well, if, uh, Charlie doesn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.68,0:50:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不介意 - 太好了{\r}\N- I don't mind. - Swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.02,0:50:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 再见牛顿太太 - 再见{\r}\N- Goodbye, then, Mrs Newton. - Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.52,0:50:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 六点半好吗? - 六点半{\r}\N- 6:30? - 6:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.02,0:51:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 好的再见 - 再见{\r}\N- OK. Goodbye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.23,0:51:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 再见桑德斯先生 再见{\r}\N- Bye, Mr Saunders. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.11,0:51:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再见{\r}\NGoodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.11,0:51:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看来他是一个 不错的年轻人啊{\r}\NHe seems like a nice young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.66,0:51:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不是要和 卡芙琳去看电影吗?{\r}\NBut I thought you were going to the movies with Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.62,0:51:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会告诉她我有点不舒服{\r}\NOh, I'll tell her I don't feel well or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.35,0:51:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你好啊查莉 - 你们好啊卡芙琳雪莉{\r}\N- Hello, Charlie. - Well... hello, Catherine. Hello, Shirley.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.77,0:51:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你们好 - 这位是格翰他刚来这里{\r}\N- Hello. - This is Jack Graham. He's in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.23,0:51:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你好 - 你好{\r}\N- How do you do? - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.23,0:51:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你的喉咙好点了吗查莉? - 好很多了谢谢{\r}\N- How's your throat, Charlie? - Oh, much better. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.86,0:51:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}比尔在问你的事呢{\r}\NBill Forest was asking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.11,0:51:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢比尔?{\r}\NOh. Bill Forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.74,0:51:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再见了{\r}\NWell, uh... goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.03,0:51:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 再见 - 再见{\r}\N- Bye. - Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.63,0:52:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道你其实是什么人{\r}\NI know what you are, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.88,0:52:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是侦探{\r}\NYou're a detective. There's something the matter and you're a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.59,0:52:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 有些事情是侦探会做的 - 听我说查莉{\r}\N- Charlie, listen. - I don't want to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.22,0:52:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不想听你们根本 就不是来做调查{\r}\NWhy, you're not on a survey at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.89,0:52:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你对我们说谎 你们骗了我妈妈{\r}\NYou lied to us. You lied to Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.89,0:52:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们只是想进我们家里{\r}\NYou just wanted to get in our house. Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.23,0:52:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就是那样{\r}\NThat's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.19,0:52:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们为什么要骗我们?{\r}\NWhat do you want with us? Why are you here, lying to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.56,0:52:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉你要听我说 你一定要相信我{\r}\NLook, Charlie, you've got to listen to me. You've got to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.73,0:52:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说谎也要相信你吗?{\r}\NWhen you've done nothing but lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.74,0:52:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道你并不是 想和我约会{\r}\NAnd you probably didn't want to take me out at all the way I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.61,0:52:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你只是想问我很多问题{\r}\NYou just wanted to ask me a lot of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.78,0:52:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我有那样做吗有吗?{\r}\NHave I asked you a lot of questions? Have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.79,0:52:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好了我的确是侦探 还做得很糟糕{\r}\NAlright, I'm a detective. A pretty bad one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.33,0:52:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你听我说几句好吗?{\r}\NNow, won't you even listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.33,0:52:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 为什么你要骗我? - 我必须那样做{\r}\N- Why should I when you lied to me? - I had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.79,0:52:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我来这里的目的 是为了一个男人不是你{\r}\NWhen I came here to find a man, I hadn't counted on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.63,0:52:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不是你妈妈和你家人 - 一个男人?什么男人?{\r}\N- I hadn't counted on your family. - Find a man? What man?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.63,0:52:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们在追踪一个在逃的人{\r}\NThere's a man loose in this country. We're after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.30,0:52:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们知道的很少 连他的样子都不知道{\r}\NWe don't know much. We don't even know what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.81,0:52:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉你对你叔叔了解有多少?{\r}\NCharlie, think. How much do you know about your uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.98,0:53:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他是我妈妈的弟弟 他有什么问题?{\r}\NWhy, he's my mother's brother. What's he got to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.27,0:53:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们要找的人 可能是你叔叔{\r}\NThis man we want may be your uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.44,0:53:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢我不相信 别再烦着我{\r}\NOh, I don't believe you. Go away and leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.28,0:53:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们追踪的那个男人 很可能就是你叔叔{\r}\NWe're after one man. Your uncle may be that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.91,0:53:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但在东部还有 另一个男人在被追捕{\r}\NBut in the East, there's another man who's being hunted too,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.49,0:53:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}从麻省到缅因 他可能就是那个人{\r}\Nthrough Massachusetts and into Maine. He may be the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.08,0:53:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我叔叔没做什么{\r}\NMy uncle hasn't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.50,0:53:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他知道那会对我妈妈不好{\r}\NHe knows it would kill my mother if he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.42,0:53:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他是我妈妈的弟弟 就像罗杰和我一样{\r}\NHe's her younger brother, just like Roger is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.30,0:53:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们为什么不把 在东部那人捉了?{\r}\NWhy don't they arrest that man in the East?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.38,0:53:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们为什么还要烦我们?{\r}\NWhy don't you go away and leave us alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.80,0:53:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉我们晚餐时 谈起各自的亲人...{\r}\NCharlie, when we were eating tonight and talking about our folks
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.97,0:53:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就像平常人一样{\r}\Nand what we'd done and how we felt, we were like two ordinary people.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.60,0:53:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们都在同样环境中成长{\r}\NWe'd been brought up about the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.73,0:53:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们彼此都有好感 - 噢现在已不重要了{\r}\N- You liked me and I liked you. - Oh, it doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.82,0:53:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么不重要这点才重要{\r}\NWhat do you mean, "It doesn't matter"? It's the only thing that does.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.15,0:53:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果不是你的叔叔...{\r}\NIf it weren't for you, you don't think I ' d care
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.57,0:53:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我早就把他逮捕了 知道吗?{\r}\Nhow or where I caught up with your uncle, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.70,0:53:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为如果他真的是我们要的人 我们就要捉住他{\r}\NBecause if he's the guy, I'm going to catch up with him. Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.12,0:54:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你必须保守秘密{\r}\NAnd you're going to keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.50,0:54:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为你是个很好的女孩 如果你知道了...{\r}\NYou're going to keep your mouth shut because you're such a nice girl
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.33,0:54:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你就会帮你叔叔{\r}\Nyou'd help if you knew your uncle was the man we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.25,0:54:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不会帮你们的 - 我知道你会的{\r}\N- I wouldn't help you. - And I know you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.22,0:54:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让我再给你一个好些的条件{\r}\NAnd I'm trying to make it easier for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.72,0:54:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你叔叔真的是那个人 我们会平静地把他从这里带走{\r}\NIf your uncle's the man we want, we'll get him out of town quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.93,0:54:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们不会在这里逮捕他 - 在这?在妈妈面前逮捕他?{\r}\N- We won't arrest him here. - Arrest him here? With mother -
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.89,0:54:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想对你说我们不会的{\r}\NI'm trying to tell you we won ' t.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.56,0:54:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 求你了查莉 - 我什么也不会说的{\r}\N- Please, Charlie. - I won't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.86,0:54:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢送我回家吧!{\r}\NOh, take me home!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.08,0:54:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}晚安查莉{\r}\NGood night, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.13,0:54:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们发现做错了 就一定很有趣{\r}\NIt's going to be funny when you find out you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.34,0:54:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}晚安{\r}\NGood night.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.87,0:55:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你好啊查莉回来了吗? - 是的爸爸{\r}\N- Hello, Charlie. Home already? - Oh, yes, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.04,0:55:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}外面空气很好 我想出去呼吸一下{\r}\NIt's so nice out, I thought I'd get some air before I went to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.30,0:55:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你最好快点回来 查理叔叔找你{\r}\NYou better run in. Your Uncle Charlie's been asking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.80,0:55:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会在后门上去的{\r}\NI think I'll just go up the back way.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.97,0:55:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我很累不是很想说话{\r}\NI- I'm tired and I don't feel like talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.97,0:55:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好的换衣服吧{\r}\NAlright. Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.56,0:55:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}小心照顾自己啊{\r}\N- Take care of yourself. - Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.52,0:55:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 晚安贺博 - 晚安查莉{\r}\N- Good night, Herb. - Good night, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.56,0:55:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}晚安查莉{\r}\NGood night, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.35,0:55:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们在说什么贺博?{\r}\NWhat were we saying, Herb? Did I notice what?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.40,0:55:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}觉得有点什么不妥吗...{\r}\NWell, did you taste anything funny
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.36,0:55:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你今晚在我家喝的咖啡?{\r}\Nabout that coffee you had at my house this evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.65,0:55:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有啊{\r}\NNo. It tasted all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.90,0:55:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这就对了 那里面有点不同{\r}\NThat's what I mean. It wasn't all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.16,0:56:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 放了什么? - 一点苏打水{\r}\N- Put something in it? - Put a little soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.03,0:56:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果我放毒药的话 也是这份量{\r}\NAbout the same amount that I'd have used if I'd wanted to use poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.66,0:56:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不说我还不察觉呢{\r}\NWell, you don't say? I never tasted a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.29,0:56:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然我连苏打 也察觉不到{\r}\NOf course, I might not notice the soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.42,0:56:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}更别提无色无味的毒药{\r}\NYou'd notice the soda more than you would the poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.26,0:56:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果是的话 你现在早死了{\r}\NFor all you knew, you might just as well be dead now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.91,0:56:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 安妮还没睡吗? - 是啊{\r}\N- Aren't you asleep yet, Ann? - Uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.55,0:57:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉你在干嘛?{\r}\NCharlotte, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.97,0:57:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢我在找我看过的新闻{\r}\NOh, I'm just looking for a recipe I thought I saw,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.98,0:57:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但这已经给撕破了- -{\r}\Nbut it's just so torn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.69,0:57:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}图书馆里什么报纸都有{\r}\NThey have papers in the "libarry", new ones and old ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.98,0:57:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}柯克然小姐会帮你找的{\r}\NMiss Corcoran will get them out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.94,0:57:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就算你剪下来一点 她都不会发现的{\r}\NShe won't even notice if you cut out a little, bitty recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.65,0:57:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那也不是什么重要的东西{\r}\NOh, it's not that important.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.16,0:57:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}图书馆几时关门?{\r}\NWhat time does the library close?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.74,0:57:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你平时多去的话 就会知道是9点{\r}\NIf you read as much as you should, you'd know it closes at 9:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.96,0:57:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这样啊那我明天才去吧{\r}\NOh, well. If I think about it, maybe I'll go tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.46,0:57:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你该睡了{\r}\NYou really ought to go to sleep, Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.22,0:58:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}回去!回去!回去!{\r}\NGet back there! Get back! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.11,0:58:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉等一下 知道我为什么在这吗?{\r}\NJust a moment, Charlie. What do you think I am out here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.19,0:58:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起诺顿警官{\r}\NOh, I'm sorry, Mr Norton.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.32,0:58:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没事了走吧{\r}\NAlright. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.99,0:59:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢柯克然小姐 请让我进去!{\r}\NOh! Miss Corcoran, please let me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.82,0:59:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}求求你!{\r}\NOh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.54,0:59:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}太谢谢你了{\r}\NOh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.46,0:59:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉你真是的 明知道这里9点关门{\r}\NReally, Charlie. You know as well as I do the library closes at 9:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.58,0:59:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果我这次给你例外 以后还得了{\r}\NIf I make one exception, I'll have to make a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.71,0:59:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起柯克然小姐 我要找出那报纸{\r}\NI'm sorry, Mrs Corcoran, but there is something in the paper I've got to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.59,0:59:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}太令我惊讶了 你都不为别人着想{\r}\NI'm surprised at you, Charlie. No consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.13,0:59:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我只需要一分钟 - 你一大早又不来{\r}\N- Oh, I'll only be a minute. - You've got all day to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.01,0:59:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真不知道你为啥 夜晚赶来这里{\r}\NI don't know why you want to rush in here tonight like a madwoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.76,0:59:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我只给你三分钟{\r}\NI'll give you just three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.66,1:00:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老天保佑不要是坏消息{\r}\NCan't be anything really awful.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.41,1:00:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会证明他不是的{\r}\NI'll prove to him it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.46,1:00:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}第三版- -{\r}\NPage three -
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.72,1:01:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你好{\r}\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.56,1:02:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查莉在哪? - 她还在睡我不想吵醒她{\r}\N- Where's Charlie? - Still asleep. I don't want to wake her.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.03,1:02:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查莉还在睡吗? - 不她刚醒来{\r}\N- Charlie still asleep? - No, she just woke up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.62,1:02:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不该让她睡那么久 但她好像很累{\r}\NI shouldn't have let her sleep so long, but she needed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.54,1:02:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她有点不舒服 她会下来吃饭的{\r}\NShe doesn't look quite herself. She'll be down for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.65,1:02:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈妈让我来捣碎这些{\r}\NMother, let me finish mashing those.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.73,1:02:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我来弄晚餐吧{\r}\NI'll fix the rest of dinner and get it on the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.82,1:02:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你去跟查理叔叔聊吧{\r}\NYou go talk to Uncle Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.28,1:02:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你觉得怎么样? - 我没事{\r}\N- How do you feel? - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.24,1:02:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我累极了 睡得死死的{\r}\NI must have been tired. I slept like a log.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.95,1:03:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查理叔叔找你很多次了 他很喜欢你{\r}\NUncle Charlie was asking for you again. He's fond of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.33,1:03:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那年轻人也来过两次 我说你睡了{\r}\NThat nice young man came to ask after you. I told him you were asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.13,1:03:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我又恢复精神了 这肉汁弄好了吗?{\r}\NI'm rested now. Is the gravy made?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.30,1:03:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你又在哼那华尔兹曲了{\r}\NNow you're humming that waltz. Please don't hum that tune anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.18,1:03:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我好不容易才忘了它{\r}\NI've just got it out of my head and don't want it started again.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.31,1:03:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要再哼了{\r}\NPlease remember, don't hum that tune.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.02,1:03:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要每次都站起来{\r}\NAnd don't keep getting up every few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.48,1:03:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只要像个淑女那样 静静坐着{\r}\NYou just sit there and be a real lady.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.23,1:03:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那好吧 至少我能把汤端出去{\r}\NAlright, if you say so, but at least I can carry in the soup.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.69,1:03:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}罗杰快洗手! 祖查理吃饭了{\r}\NRoger, wash your hands! Joe. Charles. Dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.99,1:03:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈妈安妮我说过 不要把东西挂在耳后{\r}\N- Mama - - Ann, don't put things behind your ear.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.12,1:03:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别低声说谁都知道 你在说坏话{\r}\NAnd don't whisper. Anyone could hear you a block away.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.42,1:03:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我能跟你坐吗?{\r}\NMay I sit by you at the table?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.17,1:03:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}跟我?我还以为 你想跟查理叔叔坐呢{\r}\NBy me? I should think you'd want to sit by Uncle Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.38,1:03:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不我想跟你坐 - 为什么想换?{\r}\N- No, I want to sit by you. - Why do you want to change?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.80,1:03:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈妈就让她换吧{\r}\NMother, let her change if she wants to.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.80,1:03:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}罗杰说不介意{\r}\NRoger doesn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.05,1:04:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他当然不介意 但查理叔叔会不能{\r}\NNo, certainly not. Uncle Charlie might think... Certainly not.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.22,1:04:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 妈妈让她换吧 - 好吧安妮总是有怪念头{\r}\N- Mother, let her change. - OK, but Ann has some foolish ideas.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.02,1:04:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们都去饭厅吧{\r}\NGo in the dining room, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.99,1:04:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么事了? 安妮不跟我坐了吗?{\r}\NWhat's going on here? Have I lost my little girl?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.16,1:04:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}罗杰想跟你坐{\r}\NRoger wanted to sit next to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.70,1:04:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想让孩子们换换座位{\r}\Nand I thought it would be nice if the children took turns.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.92,1:04:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我才不想- -  - 不想什么罗杰?{\r}\N- I never... - Never what, Roger?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.75,1:04:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没事安妮快来帮我{\r}\N- Nothing. - Come, Ann. Come and help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.26,1:04:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}祖!   我不该把报纸 带到饭桌上没特别的新闻{\r}\NJoe! I brought it in by mistake. Nothing special in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.55,1:04:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查理想看一下吗? - 谢谢祖{\r}\N- Want to look at the headlines, Charles? - Thank you, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.89,1:04:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}罗杰喝汤不要发出声音{\r}\NRoger, don't make so much noise with your soup.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.81,1:04:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果他能像马一样 把嘴唇贴近点就好了{\r}\NIf he holds his lips together, he could draw it carefully, like a horse.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.44,1:04:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 别那么恶心 - 我能把面包沾进去吗?{\r}\N- Don't be disgusting. - May I dip my bread in it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.44,1:04:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查莉呢? - 她在准备晚餐{\r}\N- Where's Charlie? - She wanted to serve dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.53,1:05:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 她很快就来 - 说得对祖{\r}\N- She ' II be in in a minute. - You're right, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.37,1:05:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没什么特别新闻 她来了!{\r}\NNothing special tonight. Oh, here she is!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.70,1:05:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我可爱的外甥女来了 - 我想知道你睡了多久{\r}\N- Here ' s my girl. - How many hours did you sleep?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.75,1:05:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只要你告诉我什么时候睡{\r}\NIf you could tell me the exact minute you went to sleep,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.71,1:05:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你什么时候醒 如果你中途有醒来...{\r}\Nthe exact minute you woke up, if you woke up in between
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.13,1:05:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那你醒了多久{\r}\Nand how long you stayed awake each time you woke up,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.13,1:05:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}然后我就能准确告诉你{\r}\Nthen I could tell you exactly -
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.09,1:05:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你今晚准睡不着 没人能睡一整天的{\r}\NYou won't sleep tonight. Nobody who sleeps all day can.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.93,1:05:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我昨晚做梦{\r}\NI slept all right, and I kept dreaming,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.98,1:05:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}关于你的噩梦 查理叔叔{\r}\Nperfect nightmares about you, Uncle Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.90,1:05:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}关于我的噩梦?{\r}\NNightmares about me?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.23,1:05:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你在火车上 想躲避某些东西...{\r}\NYou were on a train, running away from something
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.15,1:05:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我很高兴看到你在火车上{\r}\Nand when I saw you on the train, I felt terribly happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.87,1:05:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看到查理叔叔在 火车上又怎会高兴呢?{\r}\NHow could you feel happy seeing Uncle Charlie on a train?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.29,1:05:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我才不要他离开呢 我要他留在这{\r}\NI don't want to see him on a train. I hope he stays here forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.04,1:05:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他始终要走 我们要面对现实{\r}\NWell, he has to leave sometime. We have to face the facts.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.29,1:05:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我欣赏面对现实的人{\r}\NI like people who face facts.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.05,1:06:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们也不一定 要遇到那些事{\r}\NWell, we're not going to face any such facts as those.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.97,1:06:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安妮你要看笑话吗?{\r}\NOh, Ann, would you like to see the funnies?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.01,1:06:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我长大了 一个星期还看两本书{\r}\NI'm too old for funnies. I read two books a week. I took a sacred oath I would.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.48,1:06:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而且在饭桌上 阅读是不礼貌的{\r}\NBesides, no one's allowed to read at the table. It isn't polite.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.27,1:06:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要顶撞长辈!{\r}\NDon't correct your elders!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.11,1:06:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不关她事艾玛 是我忘了{\r}\NShe's right, Emmy. I'm forgetting my manners.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.36,1:06:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}祖我不是说你带报纸来{\r}\NJoe, I'm going to blame this paper on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.45,1:06:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}罗杰去冰箱 找那红瓶子的酒来{\r}\NRoger, go to the icebox and bring me a big, red bottle you'll find there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.78,1:06:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在能把报纸扔走 爸爸读过你也读过{\r}\NYou can throw the paper away. Dad's read it, you've read it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.12,1:06:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今晚我们 也不玩什么游戏了{\r}\NWe don't need to play any games with it tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.87,1:06:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安妮帮查莉 把水果拿出来{\r}\NAnn, you can help Charlie carry the vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.54,1:06:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我准备晚餐 时就看到那瓶酒{\r}\NI saw that bottle when I was getting dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.55,1:06:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}圣.波罗说过“ 为了胃部着想而喝点酒”{\r}\NSt Paul said, "Take a little wine for thy stomach's sake. "
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.72,1:06:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}餐酒... 听起来多暧昧!{\r}\NWine for dinner sounds so gay!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.80,1:06:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}记得老琼斯的大女儿 结婚时的酒吗?{\r}\NRemember they had the champagne when the oldest Jones girl got married?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.64,1:06:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是正宗 法国勃艮第红酒啊{\r}\NThis is sparkling burgundy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.18,1:06:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只要一口 我就知道是勃艮第红酒{\r}\NOne sip and I'll be calling it "sparkling burgledy. "
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.90,1:06:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我还是不要喝了{\r}\NMaybe I'd better not take any.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.23,1:07:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢...进口的{\r}\NOh... imported.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.78,1:07:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}法国进口和那些斜纹?{\r}\NImported Frankie and his tweeds?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.49,1:07:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他把斜纹刻在拐杖上{\r}\NAnd his loaded cane.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.74,1:07:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他把什么都刻上去!{\r}\NHis loaded everything!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.12,1:07:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}罗杰拿四苹杯子出来{\r}\NRoger, go get four of the small glasses with stems.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.84,1:07:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我答应俱乐部的格林太太 你给女士们演讲{\r}\NCharles, I promised Mrs Greene of our club that you'd talk to the ladies.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.63,1:07:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我讲什么好呢? 一般都是时事和见闻{\r}\NWhat am I going to talk about? Travel or current events?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.43,1:07:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要讲时事 我们听得多了{\r}\NOh, not current events. We get current events.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.76,1:07:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么类型的观众?{\r}\NWho'll my audience be?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.02,1:07:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}像我一样的家庭主妇{\r}\NOh, women like myself. Busy with our homes, most of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.48,1:07:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这城镇的女士们都很忙{\r}\NWomen keep busy in towns like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.90,1:07:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在大城市就不同 中年的寡妇{\r}\NIn the cities it's different. Middle-aged widows, husbands dead,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.32,1:07:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她们死去的丈夫 穷尽一生积累财富{\r}\Nhusbands who ' ve spent their lives making fortunes, working and working,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.45,1:07:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}留下一大笔钱给 愚蠢的妻子{\r}\Nand then they die and leave their money to their wives, their silly wives.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.87,1:07:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这些没用的妻子们怎么做?{\r}\NAnd what do the wives do, these useless women?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.67,1:08:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她们出入 最豪华奢侈的酒店{\r}\NYou see them in the best hotels every day by the thousands,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.42,1:08:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}吃喝玩乐 挥霍度日{\r}\Ndrinking the money, eating the money,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.92,1:08:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}花钱如流水{\r}\Nlosing the money at bridge, playing all day and all night,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.18,1:08:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}浑身都是铜臭味{\r}\Nsmelling of money.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.35,1:08:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}唯一值得引以为荣的 是她们的珠宝{\r}\NProud of their jewellery, but of nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.14,1:08:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}讨厌衰老肥胖 贪心的女人{\r}\NHorrible, faded, fat, greedy women.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.98,1:08:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但她们是人啊! 活生生的人啊!{\r}\NBut they're alive! They're human beings.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.52,1:08:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是吗?是吗查莉?{\r}\NAre they? Are they, Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.78,1:08:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她们不像贪得 无厌的动物吗?怎么样?{\r}\NAre they human, or are they fat, wheezing animals? Hm?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.20,1:08:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}动物变老 肥得不能动了又怎么样?{\r}\NAnd what happens to animals when they get too fat and too old?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.70,1:08:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我好像在这就演讲了{\r}\NWell, I seem to be making my speech right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.46,1:08:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要在俱乐部说这些! 你会被赶下台的{\r}\NDon't talk about women like that in front of my club! You'll be lynched.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.42,1:08:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}波特太太也去 她跟我提起你{\r}\NThat nice Mrs Potter's going to be there. She was asking me about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.63,1:08:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}格林把她带去俱乐部 演讲后我帮你介绍{\r}\NThe Greenes are bringing her here to the party I'm having for you afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.97,1:08:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}祖贺博来了{\r}\NJoe, it's Herbert.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.14,1:08:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他总是在我们吃饭时来{\r}\NHe always comes when we're eating.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.69,1:09:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}晚安牛顿太太{\r}\NGood evening, Mrs Newton.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.02,1:09:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 晚安奥克里先生 - 晚安{\r}\N- Good evening, Mr Oakley. - Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.65,1:09:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}贺博你妈妈还好吗?{\r}\NWell, Herb, how's your mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.49,1:09:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢一般吧{\r}\NOh, she's just middling.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.66,1:09:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 吃饭了吗? - 一小时前吃过了{\r}\N- Had your dinner? - Oh, I had mine an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.66,1:09:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们果然新潮 这么晚才吃饭啊{\r}\NYou folks are getting pretty stylish. Having dinner later every evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.46,1:09:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哈哈!{\r}\NHa ha!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.05,1:09:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 祖 - 怎么啦?{\r}\N- Joe. - Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.18,1:09:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 祖我摘了些蘑菇 - 你没告诉我{\r}\N- Joe, I-I picked some mushrooms. - You don't say?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.97,1:09:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}蘑菇令你想起什么吗?{\r}\NMushrooms mean anything to you, Joe?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.85,1:09:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在外面吃的肉排 还不如这个美味呢{\r}\NI eat 'em on my steak when I'm out and the meat's not good enough as it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.23,1:09:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我送你些蘑菇 你会吃吗?{\r}\NIf I brought you some mushrooms, would you eat 'em?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.57,1:09:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}可能会吧 为什么这样说?{\r}\NSuppose I would. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.57,1:09:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对了我最多只会 被判一般杀人罪{\r}\NThen I've got it. The worst I'd be accused of would be manslaughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.78,1:09:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}造成意外死亡 干净利落{\r}\NDoubt if I'd get that. Accidental death, pure and simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.70,1:10:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一篮子的蘑菇里... 只有两三个有毒{\r}\NA basket of good mushrooms and... two or three poisonous ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.29,1:10:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不无知的陪审团 只会注意有毒的{\r}\NNo, no. Innocent party might get the poisonous ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.30,1:10:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在刮胡子时想到一方法{\r}\NI thought of something better when I was shaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.88,1:10:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}浴盆把你倒挂着 而你的腿放在外面 这有人做过了但兵不厌诈{\r}\NA bath tub. Pull the legs out from under you, hold you down.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.85,1:10:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们怎么了?{\r}\NOh, what's the matter with you two?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.98,1:10:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}非得整天都说着杀人吗?{\r}\NDo you always have to talk about killing people?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.65,1:10:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们不是说杀其他人{\r}\NWe're not talking about killing people.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.81,1:10:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}贺博想杀我 而我想杀他{\r}\NHerb's talking about killing me, and I'm talking about killing him.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.98,1:10:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是你爸爸的娱乐方式{\r}\NIt's your father's way of relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.11,1:10:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他就不能用其他方式吗?{\r}\NCan't he find some other way to relax?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.40,1:10:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}除了研究毒药 就不能有点安宁吗?{\r}\NCan't we have a little peace and quiet without dragging in poisons all the time?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.24,1:10:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉!她在胡说八道{\r}\NCharlie! She doesn ' t make sense talking like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.41,1:10:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真令人担心罗杰 找她回来{\r}\NI'm worried about her. Roger, bring her back.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.92,1:10:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我跟着她 你们继续吃{\r}\NI'll go. You stay and finish dinner. I'll catch up with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.21,1:10:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她怎么了?{\r}\NWhat's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.64,1:11:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 对不起诺顿警官 - 你总是在街上乱跑{\r}\N- Excuse me, Mr Norton. - You're always running around at night.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.94,1:11:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你昨晚匆匆忙忙去哪? - 只是有点事做{\r}\N- Where were you hurrying to last night? - Just doing an errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.90,1:11:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这位是你的叔叔吗? - 是的{\r}\N- Is this your uncle I've heard about? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.36,1:11:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 诺顿警官这是查理叔叔 - 很高兴认识你你叫?{\r}\N- Uncle Charlie, Mr Norton. - Glad to know you. What's the name?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.82,1:11:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查理.奥克里 很高兴认识你{\r}\NOakley. Charles Oakley. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.29,1:11:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}管好你的外甥女 下次我可要给她开罚单{\r}\NBetter keep your eye on your niece. I'll have to give her a ticket for speeding.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.83,1:11:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在马路上横冲直撞 是违法的知道吗?{\r}\N- City ordinance about running. - Hear that, Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.29,1:11:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要知法犯法 我会看好她的了{\r}\NDon't want to break the law. I'll take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.00,1:11:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}晚安{\r}\N- Good night. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.51,1:11:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉怎么了? 发生什么事了?{\r}\NWhat's the matter, Charlie? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.35,1:11:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我要跟你谈谈 - 你又弄痛我了{\r}\N- I want to talk to you. - You're hurting my arm again.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.15,1:11:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 跟我来 - 不我没来过这些地方{\r}\N- Come in here with me. - I can't. I don't go to places like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.32,1:11:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来{\r}\NGo on in.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.67,1:12:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 带我来这干嘛? - 在哪里又有什么关系呢?{\r}\N- Why'd you bring me here? - What does it matter where we are?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.67,1:12:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你好查莉 - 你好{\r}\NHello, Charlie. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.67,1:12:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}路易斯你好查理叔叔 这是路易斯.菲治你好{\r}\NHello, Louise. Uncle Charlie, Louise Finch.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.88,1:12:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 这是我的叔叔 - 我是查莉的同学{\r}\N- This is my uncle. - I was in Charlie's class in school.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.60,1:12:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没想过你会来这里{\r}\NI sure was surprised to see you come in. I never thought I'd see you here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.89,1:12:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我来这里有两周了{\r}\NI been here two weeks. Lost my job over at Kern's.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.02,1:12:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在全镇一半的酒吧干过 要点什么?{\r}\NI've been in half the restaurants in town. What'll you have, Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.11,1:12:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不了给她一杯 姜汁我要白兰地{\r}\N- Nothing, thank you. - A ginger ale for her, a brandy for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.53,1:12:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查莉怎么了 - 怎么了?{\r}\N- Well, Charlie? - Well?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.20,1:12:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道很多吗? 那家伙告诉你些东西{\r}\NThink you know something, don't you? That young fellow told you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.37,1:12:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}杰克?凭什么说 他知道你的事?{\r}\NJack? Why should he know anything about you?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.75,1:12:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查莉我不想 我们之间有什么误会{\r}\NCharlie, something's come between us. I don't want that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.72,1:12:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为我们是老朋友啊 而且...{\r}\NWhy, we're old friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.55,1:13:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们就像双胞胎{\r}\NMore than that. We're like twins.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.89,1:13:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 是你自己说 - 查理叔叔别碰我{\r}\N- You said so yourself. - Don't touch me, Uncle Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.85,1:13:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他跟你说了什么?{\r}\NWhat did that boy tell you?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.86,1:13:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他没说什么 我也想他不知道你的事{\r}\NHe's got nothing to do with it. I hope he never knows anything about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.53,1:13:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉 你真是细心可爱的女孩{\r}\NCharlie, you're a pretty understanding sort of girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.54,1:13:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你听到 关于我的传闻{\r}\NIf you've heard some little things about me,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.37,1:13:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想你肯定 不会把它当真{\r}\NI guess you're a woman of the world enough to overlook them.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.67,1:13:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}人人都看出 你是家里的支柱{\r}\NYou're the head of your family, Charlie. Anyone can see that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.14,1:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我老了我十六岁 就开始到处漂泊{\r}\NI'm not so old. I've been chasing around the globe since I was sixteen.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.73,1:13:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我做了些蠢事{\r}\NI guess I've done some pretty foolish things,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.31,1:13:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}犯了愚蠢的错误{\r}\Nmade some pretty foolish mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.02,1:13:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没什么大不了 只是...可笑的错误{\r}\NNothing serious, just... foolish.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.54,1:14:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉别妄自猜测{\r}\NOh, Charlie, now, don't start imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.63,1:14:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你怎么能做出这种事? 你是我的叔叔{\r}\NHow could you do such things? You're my uncle,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.01,1:14:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我妈的弟弟{\r}\Nmy mother's brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.93,1:14:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们都认为 你是很成功的人{\r}\NWe thought you were the most wonderful man in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.85,1:14:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 世界上最成功的人 - 查莉你知道什么?{\r}\N- The most wonderful and the best. - Charlie, what do you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.41,1:14:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让你们久等了 我们真的很忙{\r}\NI'm sorry I was so long. We're awful busy.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.29,1:14:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是谁的? 不是很漂亮吗?{\r}\NWhose is it? Ain't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.00,1:14:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我一直都想 拥有这样的戒指{\r}\NI'd just die for a ring like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.92,1:15:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这戒指简直让我目眩{\r}\NYes sir, for a ring like that, I'd just about die.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.97,1:15:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我最爱珠宝- - 真的珠宝{\r}\NI love jewellery, real jewellery.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.43,1:15:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我根本不用就能辩出真假{\r}\NNotice I didn't even have to ask if it was real. You can tell.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.18,1:15:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我知道 - 我要多一杯白兰地{\r}\N- I can. - Bring me another brandy.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.77,1:15:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}坐下{\r}\NSit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.11,1:15:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}坐下!{\r}\NSit down!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.99,1:15:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你认为自己知道多少?{\r}\NYou think you know something, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.28,1:15:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你以为你很聪明{\r}\NYou think you're the clever little girl who knows something.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.49,1:15:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但你不知道的还多着呢{\r}\NThere's so much you don't know. So much.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.50,1:15:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道什么?{\r}\NWhat do you know, really?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.37,1:15:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你只不过是个普通的女孩{\r}\NYou're just an ordinary little girl living in an ordinary little town.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.50,1:15:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}每天从床上醒来 无　无虑{\r}\NYou wake up every day and know there's nothing in the world to trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.84,1:15:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}平平淡淡地过日子...{\r}\NYou go through your ordinary little day.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.68,1:15:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}晚上睡在安稳的床 做些无聊的梦{\r}\NAt night, you sleep your ordinary sleep filled with peaceful, stupid dreams.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.10,1:15:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是我给你带来噩梦{\r}\NAnd I brought you nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.10,1:16:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对吗?还是一个谎言?{\r}\NOr did I? Or was it a silly, inexpert, little lie?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.77,1:16:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你生活在梦境里 看不到现实{\r}\NYou live in a dream. You're a sleepwalker, blind.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.28,1:16:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道外面的世界是怎样吗?{\r}\NHow do you know what the world is like?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.95,1:16:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你能想像那就像 猪圈般肮脏吗?{\r}\NDo you know the world is a foul sty?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.03,1:16:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道周围是带着 面具的卑贱小人吗?{\r}\NDo you know if you ripped the fronts off houses, you'd find swine?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.66,1:16:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这个该死的世界 有谁在乎发生什么?{\r}\NThe world's a hell. What does it matter what happens in it?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.21,1:16:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}醒醒吧查莉 你的聪明去哪了?{\r}\NWake up, Charlie. Use your wits. Learn something!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.96,1:16:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉你走了吗?{\r}\NYou goin', Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.94,1:16:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查莉你会帮我吗? - 帮你?{\r}\N- Charlie, will you help me? - Help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.07,1:16:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们身上淌着一样的血 一周前我几乎绝望{\r}\NThe same blood flows through our veins. I was at the end of my rope.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.91,1:16:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我太累了我受够了{\r}\NOh, I'm so tired. There's an end to the running a man can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.41,1:17:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你没法想像那种累 我准备- -{\r}\NYou'll never know what it's like to be so tired. I was going to...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.63,1:17:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯...我想离开这里 帮帮我查莉{\r}\NThen I got the idea of coming out here. It's my last chance, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.14,1:17:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}给我一次机会{\r}\NGive it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.26,1:17:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}格翰和那个家伙不知道{\r}\NGraham and the other fellow, they don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.39,1:17:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果抓到东部的那个 嫌疑犯我就- -{\r}\NThere's a man in the east they suspect, and if they get him, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.60,1:17:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉给我一次机会{\r}\NCharlie, give me this last chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.27,1:17:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧那你走!{\r}\NTake your chance. Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.90,1:17:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会走的查莉 给我几天时间{\r}\NI'll go, Charlie. Just give me a few days.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.86,1:17:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为你妈妈着想 她知道后会疯的{\r}\NThink of your mother. It'll kill your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.57,1:17:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道她会受不了的{\r}\NYes, it would kill my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.04,1:17:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那你几天后要离开这里{\r}\NTake your few days. See that you get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.50,1:17:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道如果 我被抓了后果是什么?{\r}\NYou realise what it'll mean if they get me?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.83,1:17:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}坐电椅{\r}\NThe electric chair.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.00,1:17:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉全靠你了 你要帮我啊{\r}\NCharlie, you've got to help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.72,1:17:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说我们不仅是叔叔 与外甥女关系{\r}\NYou said yourself we're no ordinary uncle and niece, no matter what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.10,1:17:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你先进去我跟着来{\r}\NYou go in. I'll be in in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.03,1:18:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 家是最好的地方 - 查莉呢?{\r}\N- Home, sweet home. - Where's Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.95,1:18:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 她在外面别担心 - 她怎么了?{\r}\N- She's outside. Don't worry about her. - What was the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.04,1:18:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她有点烦躁 我让她去散散心{\r}\NShe was a little edgy. I persuaded her to go for a walk. She's calmer now.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.62,1:18:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 那就好给你留了甜品 - 冰淇淋苏打{\r}\N- I'm so glad. I've saved dessert for you. - We had an ice-cream soda.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.09,1:18:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢!你快点上床吧!{\r}\NOops-a-daisy! Off to bed you go!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.37,1:18:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 罗杰过来! - 不!{\r}\N- Roger, come here! - No!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.71,1:19:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我来对付她 嘘!安妮!{\r}\NThere's my girl. Psst! Ann!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.54,1:19:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你好! 你一定是藏着什么{\r}\NHello! You must be trying to hide or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.80,1:19:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我没有 - 只有藏着东西的人才会说嘘{\r}\N- We're not hiding. - People who are hiding say "psst".
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.05,1:19:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不想在星期天吵闹 - 听着安妮{\r}\N- We just don't want to yell on Sunday. - Look, Ann.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.85,1:19:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}叫你姐姐来一下 小声点我们在这等{\r}\NAsk your sister to run over here. Just ask her quietly. We'll wait here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.68,1:19:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我爸爸跟你爸爸有过节吗? - 我爸爸?{\r}\N- Did my father have a feud with yours? - My father?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.40,1:19:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不然你不会 瞒着别人叫她来{\r}\NBecause if they didn't, there's no sense in my asking Charlotte quietly.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.57,1:19:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈妈不介意的 她说女人就该生儿育女{\r}\NMama won't care. She thinks girls ought to marry and settle down.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.24,1:19:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我读过一本书- -  - 叫她来吧别卖弄文才了{\r}\N- In a book I'm reading - - Just ask her, Ann. Don't be literary.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.91,1:19:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 好吧 - 记住由我来说{\r}\N- Alright. - Remember, I'm doing all the talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.79,1:19:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你好 - 你好你好凯瑟琳{\r}\N- Hello. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.63,1:19:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}早上好格翰警官{\r}\NGood morning, Mr Graham.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.17,1:19:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}凯瑟琳 这是桑德斯警官{\r}\NCatherine, this is Mr Saunders.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.34,1:19:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你好 - 你好{\r}\N- How do you do? - How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.88,1:19:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 安妮说你有事找我 - 桑德斯有事跟你说{\r}\N- Ann says you want to speak to me. - Saunders wants to.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.47,1:20:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来安妮，跟凯瑟琳说说吧{\r}\NCome on, Ann. Tell Catherine the story of Dracula.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.14,1:20:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来吧，凯瑟琳{\r}\NCome on, Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.02,1:20:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你想怎样? - 让他们走远点再说{\r}\N- What do you want? - Let them get a little bit ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.78,1:20:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想说关于 你叔叔的照片的事{\r}\NIt's about that photograph we took, the one of your uncle.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.12,1:20:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你给回他了他也许烧掉 - 不是那张{\r}\N- He probably burned it. - Not that one, he hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.66,1:20:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们给了张错误的相片{\r}\NWe gave him the wrong film.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.08,1:20:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们拿真正的照片 跟东部那边联系{\r}\NWe got the picture alright. We wired it East.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.50,1:20:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那里的证人能认出 谁是我们通缉的罪犯{\r}\NThey've got witnesses can identify the man we want from that picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.63,1:20:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 什么能认出是他? - 对了{\r}\N- What do you mean, identify him? - Just what I said.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.22,1:20:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当证人看到照片 就能知道他是否罪犯{\r}\NWhen the witnesses see that picture, we'll know whether Oakley's the man.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.59,1:20:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们准备跟那边联系 - 那查理叔叔会- -{\r}\N- We're waiting for the wire now. - And then Uncle Charlie will be -
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.81,1:20:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对了就是这样{\r}\NThat's right. That's the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.77,1:20:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}格翰想你可以让他离开 这会好点- -{\r}\NGraham thought you could get your uncle to leave town now. It would be better -
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.94,1:20:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会的一定会! 你能给多长时间?{\r}\NI've got to, haven't I? I've got to! What's the most time you'll give me?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.86,1:21:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}两小时内 我会叫他离开的!{\r}\N- Two hours. - I'll make him leave!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.57,1:21:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你为什么肯定 他是我们要找的人?{\r}\NYou seem pretty sure he's the man we want. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.49,1:21:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 没有原因我只是害怕 - 你是唯一能肯定的人{\r}\NNo reason why. I'm just scared. You're the ones who seem sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.17,1:21:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不能让这里有事 - 你知道他干过什么?{\r}\N- I couldn't bear anything happening here. - You know what he's done?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.96,1:21:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不我不想听! - 希望你知道{\r}\N- No, I don't want to hear! - Well, I want you to get this.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.63,1:21:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们想帮你 把知道的都告诉我们吧!{\r}\NWe're doing you a favour. If you know anything more about your uncle, tell us.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.10,1:21:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们还想知道 他什么时候离开{\r}\NWe also want to know when and how he leaves town.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.60,1:21:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 如果你瞒着我们- -  - 不我会告诉你的{\r}\N- If you hold out on us - - I won't. I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.06,1:21:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走多一步 你会弄伤妈妈的背{\r}\NStep on a crack, you'll break your mother's back.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.23,1:21:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们都想相信你{\r}\NI wish I knew we could trust you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.98,1:21:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我保证不会再帮他了{\r}\NI won't do anything to help him, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.24,1:21:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但你不能让 我去暗中监视他{\r}\NBut you can't ask me to spy on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.49,1:21:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们来个交易 我叫他离开{\r}\NWe've made a bargain. I'll get him to leave. That's all I'll do.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.33,1:21:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉他是危险人物 一旦离开我们视线范围- -{\r}\NThink, Charlie. The man's dangerous. If he gets away from us -
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.20,1:21:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不想知道他做什么 我会遵守诺言{\r}\NI don't want to hear what he'll do. We've made a bargain. I'll keep it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.46,1:21:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他走的时候 我会通知你{\r}\NI'll let you know when he leaves.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.17,1:22:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}万一他不是通缉犯 那有好看的{\r}\NFunny if he turned out to be the wrong man. Could be.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.34,1:22:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 安妮 - 我把妈妈的背弄伤了三次{\r}\N- Ann! - I broke my mother's back three times.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.39,1:22:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你还没说罗斯小姐 是否嫁给了有钱人...{\r}\NNot bad. You didn't finish telling me whether Miss Rose married the rich guy,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.68,1:22:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 或者她的新欢 - 你跟她那么熟啊?{\r}\N- or the one she was in love with. - How long have you two such friends?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.81,1:22:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们在玩游戏 我问她答{\r}\NOh, we play games. I ask questions. She knows all the answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.65,1:22:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}麻烦的是 我弄不懂她在胡扯什么{\r}\NThe only trouble is I can't make out what she's making up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.69,1:22:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不会胡扯，说的都是书本上的知识{\r}\NI never make up anything. I get everything from my books.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.20,1:22:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我说的都是事实{\r}\NThey're all true.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.91,1:22:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安妮来吧 我们去帮忙做饭吧再见{\r}\NCome on, Ann. We'd better get home and help with dinner. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.04,1:22:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再见再见 格翰警官桑德斯警官{\r}\N- Goodbye. - Goodbye, Mr Graham. Mr Saunders.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.71,1:22:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 再见凯瑟琳 - 再见{\r}\N- Goodbye, Catherine. - Come on, Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.96,1:22:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为啥不去摘些花 点缀一下晚餐?越简单越好{\r}\N- Why not pick flowers for the table? - Simple flowers are the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.55,1:22:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 不用是紫罗兰的 - 要是我在南方出生就好了{\r}\N- I didn't ask for orchids. - I wish I'd been born in the South.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.13,1:22:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}南方的女人很有魅力 她们戴着手套摘花{\r}\NSouthern women have a lot of charm. They pick flowers with gloves on.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.64,1:22:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 再见凯瑟琳 - 再见查莉晚饭后见{\r}\N- Goodbye, Catherine. - Goodbye, Charlie. See you after dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.35,1:22:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再见{\r}\NBye.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.94,1:22:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 安妮你好 - 你好{\r}\N- Hello, Ann. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.44,1:22:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}教堂怎么样? 够座位吗?有人要让座吗?{\r}\NHow was church, Charlie? Did you count the house? Turn anybody away?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.44,1:23:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不够了{\r}\NNo, room enough for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.95,1:23:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很好{\r}\NI'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.16,1:23:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}演出一段时间了 观众会陆续减少{\r}\NShow's been running such a long time, I thought attendance might be falling off.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.58,1:23:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}电台有什么新闻吗?{\r}\NAnything special on the noon broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.33,1:23:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说抓到了另一个 嫌疑犯- - 玛丽寡妇杀手{\r}\NThey caught that other fellow, the Merry Widow Murderer.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.79,1:23:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 真的吗?哪里? - 缅因州的波特兰{\r}\N- They did, did they? Where? - State of Maine. Portland.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.17,1:23:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不算真正的抓到 他逃避警方的追捕{\r}\NDidn't catch him exactly. He was running away from the police,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.72,1:23:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}跑进了飞机场 躲到飞机的推进器后{\r}\Nand they cornered him at the airport and he ran into the propeller of a plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.35,1:23:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 噢! - 他被切得肢离破碎{\r}\N- Oh, boy! - Cut him all to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.39,1:23:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只能从衣服辩认{\r}\NHad to identify him by his clothes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.85,1:23:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他的衣服印着“C”“O” 省略号“H”{\r}\NHis shirts were all initialled, "C," "O," apostrophe "H."
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.98,1:23:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很快就能划上句号的了{\r}\NWell, makes a good ending. Couldn't have done better myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.65,1:23:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这案子很快就结束的{\r}\NI guess that closes that case pretty final.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.07,1:23:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然不用太担心那案子{\r}\NSure does. Never cared much for that case.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.49,1:23:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我今天可要饱餐一顿啦{\r}\NWell, I think I'll go get ready for dinner. I'm hungry. I can eat a good dinner today.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.38,1:24:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉有好消息通知你 哪里能聊几句?{\r}\NCharlie, I have great news for you. Where can we talk alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.61,1:25:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}缅因州通知结束案子 你也能解脱了{\r}\NWe got a wire from Maine. We can call off the job. I'll bet you're relieved. I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.11,1:25:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢解脱了{\r}\NOh, I am relieved.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.07,1:25:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还游说你叔叔离开这 他肯定说你疯了{\r}\NYou were trying to get youruncle out. He must have thought you were crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.83,1:25:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一切都结束了 我不想再提了{\r}\NNow that it's over, I don't want to talk about it any more.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.12,1:25:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我希望假装 这一切没发生过{\r}\NI'd like to pretend the whole dreadful thing never happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.92,1:25:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你不需要假装啊 - 妈妈的手套{\r}\N- There's nothing to pretend about. - There's mother's gloves.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.25,1:25:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她总是丢三落四的{\r}\NMother and her gloves. She's always losing things.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.38,1:25:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}迟早她连你也会失去的{\r}\NAll mothers lose things. Someday, she'll be losing you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.84,1:25:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她才没有损失呢 还多了一个女婿{\r}\NMothers don't lose daughters, they gain sons.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.72,1:25:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也是但事情 总不那么如意譬如我吧{\r}\NYes, but gain isn't always the word. Now, take me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.27,1:25:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁想要个侦探做女婿?{\r}\NWho'd want a detective for a son-in-law?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.90,1:25:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我爸爸会 - 他会?{\r}\N- My father would. - He would?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.23,1:25:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你说要嫁给侦探 他会怎么反应?{\r}\NIf you told him you were going to marry a detective, he wouldn't disown you?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.70,1:25:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不一定是我啊 可以是安妮{\r}\NIt wouldn't have to be me. There's Ann.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.78,1:25:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不她跟我说要 嫁给图书管理员{\r}\NNo, Ann wants to marry a librarian. She told me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.16,1:25:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所以她经常读那么多书{\r}\NSo she'll always have plenty of books around to read.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.87,1:26:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么事了?{\r}\NWhat's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.96,1:26:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我好久没这么开怀地笑了{\r}\NI was laughing. It's been so long since I laughed.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.76,1:26:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我喜欢你笑的样子{\r}\NI like it when you laugh.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.63,1:26:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我喜欢你做的每件事{\r}\NI like it when you don't. I guess I like you whatever you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.05,1:26:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我喜欢你 - 我也喜欢你{\r}\N- I guess I like you. - I'm glad. I like you too.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.68,1:26:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有趣的是你遇见一个人 然后...爱上她{\r}\NFunny how you happen to meet someone and like them and... like them.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.06,1:26:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嗯{\r}\NMm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.11,1:26:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查莉? - 什么事?{\r}\N- Charlie? - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.07,1:26:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想有天你会 跟你爸爸说- -{\r}\NI suppose it couldn't ever really happen some day that you'd tell your father...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.82,1:26:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}要嫁给一个侦探{\r}\NYou know, about marrying someone, a detective, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.74,1:26:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不知道 - 我也不想现在告诉你{\r}\N- I don't know. - I didn't mean to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.16,1:26:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想等你把这一切 不愉快的事忘记{\r}\NI wanted to wait until you'd forgotten the mess we've been through together,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.63,1:26:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}直到你想起 我不再有恐惧和不安{\r}\Ntill you didn't think of me as part of something unpleasant and frightening.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.80,1:26:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我希望能回来告诉你{\r}\NI wanted to wait and come back and then tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.47,1:26:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我想现在就跟你说{\r}\NBut I can't help it. I want to tell you now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.93,1:26:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉我爱你{\r}\NI love you, Charlie. I love you terribly.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.68,1:27:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你介意我现在才说吗?{\r}\NI know it's no time to tell you now and I'm sorry. Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.02,1:27:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我不介意 - 你会考虑一下吗?{\r}\N- I don't mind. - Do you think you could think about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.02,1:27:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 关于你爱我? - 也许你也爱我{\r}\N- About your loving me? - And perhaps your loving me?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.99,1:27:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我希望保持朋友关系 我们是朋友{\r}\NI- I'd like us to be friends. I know that. We are friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.33,1:27:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我想保持现状 - 没有其他吗?{\r}\N- I'd like to have that to think about. - Nothing more?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.08,1:27:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道杰克 我...还不知道{\r}\NI don't know, Jack. I... just don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.50,1:27:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧 但我能回来看你吗?{\r}\NAlright. But I may come back?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.80,1:27:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢当然能一定要回啊{\r}\NOh, please come back. Please come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.38,1:27:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听着查莉{\r}\NListen, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.39,1:27:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我去到市中心的广场{\r}\NWhen I go, go back to that square in the middle of town.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.18,1:27:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是我们初次认识的地方{\r}\NTake a good look at it. That's where I first knew I loved you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.02,1:27:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真是不打不相识{\r}\NThat's where we had the fight and I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.11,1:27:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我热爱我的工作 只是那晚不喜欢{\r}\NI like my job, but I didn't like it that night.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.23,1:27:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那晚我讨厌它{\r}\NI hated it that night.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.40,1:27:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你现在讨厌它吗? - 不{\r}\N- You hate it now? - No, not now.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.28,1:28:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这像口井 我要弄个装饰品上去{\r}\NYou know, this is a swell place. I'm going to put a bronze plaque up.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.21,1:28:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这门老是自己锁上!{\r}\NThat door's always banging shut!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.54,1:28:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢!大力点!{\r}\NOh! It sticks.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.25,1:28:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}啊!{\r}\NUh!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.27,1:28:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们把自己锁在车房干嘛?{\r}\NWhat are you two locking yourselves in the garage for?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.35,1:28:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我年轻的时候是在会议室 - 奥克里先生{\r}\N- When I was young, it was the parlour. - Hello, Mr Oakley.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.73,1:28:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我在跟查莉说再见 - 在车房里?{\r}\N- I was saying goodbye to Charlie. - In the garage?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.27,1:28:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}门被锁上了 现在我也要跟你说再见了{\r}\NThe door got stuck. Now I'll have to say goodbye to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.65,1:28:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们在草坪上道别好了 不用回到车房{\r}\NLet's say goodbye out here on the lawn. No use taking a chance on the garage.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.95,1:28:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 完了吗? - 完了我会再回来的{\r}\N- Finished here? - All finished, but I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.12,1:28:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 很快就见到我的 - 噢?{\r}\N- You ' II be seeing me around. - Oh?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.70,1:28:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不是因为公事{\r}\NNot on business, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.17,1:28:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我明白 查莉是一个好女孩{\r}\NI can understand you coming back. Charlie's a fine girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.38,1:28:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她是我见过最好的女孩{\r}\NShe's the thing I love most in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.01,1:28:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说真的格翰警官 一帆风顺{\r}\NI mean it. Have a nice trip, Mr Graham.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.47,1:28:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}下次不要乱拍照了{\r}\NAnd don't take any more photographs without permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.76,1:29:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道这是人权啊?{\r}\NRights of man. You know, freedom?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.26,1:29:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们下次再讨论这个吧{\r}\NWe'll have a talk about freedom some day, Mr Oakley.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.48,1:29:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 再会 - 再会{\r}\N- Bye. - Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.49,1:29:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 记得给我写信 你有我地址吧- 嗯{\r}\NDon't forget to write. Remember, you have the addresses.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.50,1:29:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}杰克!{\r}\NJack!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.58,1:30:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还有吗?牛油水果 蔬菜还要去图书馆{\r}\NAnything else? I've got butter, fruit, green thread and go to the library.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.50,1:30:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}买些新鲜的 如果还有我会叫安妮去{\r}\NAnd whatever vegetable looks freshest. If I've forgotten anything, I'll send Ann.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.96,1:30:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好的{\r}\NAlright.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.93,1:30:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈妈!{\r}\NMother!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.89,1:30:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉!亲爱的! 你没事吧?{\r}\NCharlie! Darling! Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.39,1:30:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我绊倒了{\r}\NI tripped.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.27,1:30:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在哪里?弄伤了膝盖吗?{\r}\NOh, what is it? Is it your ankle?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.02,1:30:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没什么事 我扶住了栏杆{\r}\NI don't think I'm hurt. I grabbed the banister.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.15,1:30:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢你差点没命了!{\r}\NYou might have been killed!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.90,1:30:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}每次孩子们走这楼梯 我都很担心{\r}\NI worry myself sick every time one of you comes down these stairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.24,1:30:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}太陡峭和有点摇摆 要去修理一下{\r}\NThey're too steep and rickety. They ought to be fixed.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.28,1:30:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你真的没事?{\r}\NAre you sure you're all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.58,1:31:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查理叔叔 你什么时候走?{\r}\NWhen are you leaving, Uncle Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.58,1:31:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉一切都结束了 我想忘记它{\r}\NOh, come now. That other business, it's all over. I'd like to forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.92,1:31:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我们现在很开心啊 - 你什么时候走?{\r}\N- We're all happy here. - When are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.79,1:31:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不会走的{\r}\NI'm not going, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.96,1:31:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}暂时还不会{\r}\NNot yet. I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.34,1:31:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想在一个熟悉的环境里 安定下来{\r}\NI want to settle down. Live somewhere people know me. Put some money by.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.47,1:31:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而且成为这个家的一分子{\r}\N- Start a business. Be part of the family. - I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.14,1:31:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我知道了 - 乖乖跟我做朋友吧{\r}\NThe most sensible thing for you to do is to be friends with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.77,1:31:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我愿为你做一切事情{\r}\NI can do a lot for you, Charlie, for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.69,1:32:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不我们不要你的帮助{\r}\NNo, not you. We don't want anything from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.86,1:32:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我真希望向妈妈揭穿你 - 我知道你想什么{\r}\N- I wish I'd told my mother about you. - I know what you've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.62,1:32:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道她会怎样吗? 她感受如何?{\r}\NHow would your mother have felt? What would it do to her now?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.49,1:32:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你爸爸呢? 他在银行的差事呢?{\r}\NHow about your father? His job at the bank?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.87,1:32:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果这一切都没有了 你又怎么样?{\r}\NWhat would become of all of you if everything came out?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.71,1:32:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不用害怕 我不能告诉他们{\r}\NYou needn't be afraid. I can't tell them.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.25,1:32:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我才不怕呢 你能向谁说?谁相信你?{\r}\NBut I'm not afraid. What would you tell? Who'd believe you?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.09,1:32:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你脑子里都是想着华尔兹{\r}\NA waltz runs through your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.43,1:32:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你从戒指上的刻字 联想到报纸的新闻{\r}\NYou don't like the initials on a ring and connect it up with a newspaper clipping.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.85,1:32:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你甚至连戒指也丢了{\r}\NNow, you haven't even got the ring. I don't know what became of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.52,1:32:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你拿了 我?{\r}\N- You have it. - I?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.61,1:32:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我送给你了{\r}\NI gave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.19,1:32:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不要你在这 不要你碰我妈妈{\r}\NI don't want you here, Uncle Charlie. I don't want you to touch my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.49,1:32:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快走- - 我警告过你 不然我会亲手杀了你{\r}\NSo go away, I'm warning you. Go away, or I'll kill you myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.70,1:32:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看见了吗? 这就是我对你的感觉{\r}\NSee? That's the way I feel about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.86,1:33:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 给你祖 - 噢香水{\r}\N- Here you are, Joe. - Oh, perfume.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.53,1:33:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 清新芬芳的熏衣草 - 我知道{\r}\N- Just the fresh, clean smell of lavender. - Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.82,1:33:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 你们都那么英伟{\r}\NYou look very handsome, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.87,1:33:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我真为你们感到自豪 - 艾玛你也很迷人{\r}\N- I'm proud of the two men in my family. - Emmy, you're a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.16,1:33:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 别在孩子们说这话{\r}\NIt's a pity the children have to sit on our laps.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.91,1:33:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这裤子有点麻烦{\r}\NIt's going to be a tight squeeze. It won't do my pants any good.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.38,1:33:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 祖我想你来开车 - 我们这样分配{\r}\N- Joe, I wish you could drive. - We do it this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.09,1:33:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查莉你坐- -  - 查理叔叔可以跟爸爸坐后面...{\r}\N- Charles, you'll sit - - He can sit in the back with Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.84,1:33:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 孩子们坐在旁边 - 不可以{\r}\NThe children can fit in beside them.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.30,1:33:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们都上出租车...{\r}\NNonsense. I'm getting a cab. You all go in the taxi.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.26,1:33:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查莉和我开车 - 不查理叔叔你坐出租车{\r}\N- Charlie and I'll go in the car. - No, Uncle Charlie, you go in the taxi.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.27,1:33:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要坐出租车!{\r}\NI want to ride in the taxi!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.69,1:33:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然可以 就这么定吧{\r}\NCourse you do. So it's all arranged.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.15,1:34:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查莉去车房把车开出来 - 我想全家人坐车{\r}\N- Charlie, run out and get the car. - I'd rather drive the family.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.28,1:34:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想你在途中听听我演讲 给点意见{\r}\NI want you to hear my speech on the way. You're my severest critic.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.66,1:34:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安妮 打电话叫辆出租车来{\r}\NAnyway, we need a taxi. Ann, go call Mr Abercrombie.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.41,1:34:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈妈!{\r}\NMother!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.96,1:34:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈妈带上我 爸爸坐出租车也可以!{\r}\NMother, please ride with me. Father can take the children. Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.18,1:35:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我肯定是全场 穿得最糟糕的人{\r}\NBet I'll be the only man outside of Charles fool enough to dress up.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.64,1:35:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不会了你穿得很体面{\r}\NThen you'll be the only other on e to be correct. You look distinguished.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.98,1:35:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查理你准备好了吗? 祖你去哪?{\r}\NCharles, are you all ready? Joe, are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.52,1:35:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}等等! 我把外套带上{\r}\NWait a minute! I've got to get my overcoat.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.15,1:35:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢亲爱的快点!{\r}\NPlease, dear. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.40,1:35:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别急他们没见到 我是不会开始的{\r}\NTake your time, Emmy. They can't start till I get there.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.69,1:35:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这里有点冷{\r}\NIt's getting chilly in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.99,1:35:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这里是圣罗莎{\r}\NKSRO, Santa Rosa,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.49,1:35:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}加州的新闻联播{\r}\Nwith studios in Vallejo and Santa Rosa, California.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.95,1:35:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}放点音乐吧{\r}\NMay as well have a little music while we wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.83,1:35:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}俄勒冈州警察局 把研究范围缩小{\r}\NOregon State Police pressed theirsearch today for five -
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.38,1:35:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢!一定要那么大声吗?{\r}\NOh! Does it have to be so loud?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.50,1:35:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把低音听清楚点{\r}\NGets the lower tones better.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.55,1:35:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我喜欢大声点! 太小声我听不到!{\r}\NI likeit loud! If the music's too soft, I can't tell what they're playing.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.05,1:35:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果我有一支乐队 肯定要组成87人{\r}\NIf I have a band, I'm a-least have 87 men.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.47,1:36:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}救命!有人被困在车房{\r}\NHelp, everybody! Somebody's caught in the garage.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.56,1:36:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那里令人窒息! 那门开不了{\r}\NThey're suffocating! There's something wrong with the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.73,1:36:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}祖!{\r}\NJoe!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.67,1:36:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让我来抱她{\r}\NI'll take her. I've got her.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.43,1:36:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}祖从我衣柜里 拿瓶酒来快点{\r}\NJoe, there's some whisky on my bureau. Get it quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.89,1:36:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查莉查莉 - 查莉?{\r}\N- Charlie. Charlie. Dear Charlie. - Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.68,1:36:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}艾玛擦擦她的腿 罗杰给她扇凉{\r}\NEmmy, rub her feet. Roger, run get something to fan her with.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.85,1:36:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉!{\r}\NCharlie!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.40,1:36:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安妮不要这样{\r}\NAnn, don't, dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.11,1:36:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉?查莉 你想说什么?{\r}\NCharlie? What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.16,1:37:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走开{\r}\NGo away.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.41,1:37:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走开{\r}\NGo away.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.58,1:37:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}艾玛她需要你{\r}\NEmmy, she wants you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.75,1:37:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在这 亲爱的妈妈在这{\r}\NI'm here, darling. Here's mother. That's right, my baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.54,1:37:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没事了 你真勇敢来...{\r}\NThat's right, my brave little girl. Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.55,1:37:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 喝一口 - 不- - 我没事{\r}\N- Take a little sip of this. - No, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.09,1:37:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 祖叫菲利医生来 - 我没事只想站起来{\r}\N- Joe, call Dr Phillips. - No, I'm all right. I just want to get up.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.01,1:37:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉你很走运 有人把车开着{\r}\NYou had a wonderful escape. Someone must have left the motor running.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.14,1:37:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我找不到钥匙关上它 - 我进去时找到了{\r}\N- I couldn't find the key to turn it off. - The key was there when I went in.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.86,1:37:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}幸亏我路过{\r}\NLucky thing I passed by.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.23,1:37:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她差点没命 全靠你知道该怎么做{\r}\NShe might have died. You saved her. You knew just what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.95,1:37:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我也不知道怎会经过 - 把演讲取消吧{\r}\N- Don't know how I happened across her. - We'll put the lecture off.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.32,1:37:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不你们都快去车来了{\r}\NOh, yes, there is. I want you all to go. There's the cab now.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.00,1:37:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢不行我要在这{\r}\NOh, I couldn't. I just couldn't go.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.87,1:37:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁在车房发现我?{\r}\NWh-Who found me in the garage?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.34,1:37:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}贺博听到你在拍门{\r}\NHerb heard you beating on the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.80,1:37:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在后院经过 听到拍门声{\r}\NI was coming across the backyard and I heard gaspin' and bangin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.97,1:38:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我就知道里面肯定有人在{\r}\NI figured there must be a human bein' in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.14,1:38:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 贺博真聪明 - 真幸运{\r}\N- Quick thinking, Herb. - Lucky thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.47,1:38:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}贺博你刚好 经过救了我{\r}\NI'm glad you happened to be going by, Herb.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.06,1:38:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来妈妈{\r}\NCome on, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.56,1:38:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我- 我想陪你{\r}\NI- I want to stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.52,1:38:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不想演讲了 一想到查莉有危险{\r}\NI don't feel like making a speech now, when I think what might have happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.32,1:38:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我没事 坐下来歇会儿就行了{\r}\NI'm all right. I just want to sit on the porch a while and get the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.45,1:38:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不亲爱的让我陪你{\r}\NNo, darling, I won't hear of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.45,1:38:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真的没事 我在家准备晚会了{\r}\NI'm alright, really. I'd rather stay home and get things ready for the party.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.66,1:38:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}亲爱的让我留下来{\r}\NDarling, I want to stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.67,1:38:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}贺博你带罗杰好吗? 安妮跟我们坐{\r}\NHerb, will you take Roger? Ann, you come with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.30,1:38:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真奇怪 首先是楼梯有意外- -{\r}\NI just don't understand it. First the stairs and...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.91,1:39:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}格翰先生不在?{\r}\NMr Graham isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.41,1:39:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是弗雷斯诺的 史都华旅馆吗?{\r}\NThis is the Hotel Stewart in Fresno, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.75,1:39:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你没见过他?{\r}\NAnd you don't expect him?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.38,1:39:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那好了谢谢你{\r}\NI see. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.05,1:39:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他不在? 谢谢再见{\r}\NHe isn't there? Thank you very much. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.72,1:39:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你能告诉我怎样找到他吗?{\r}\NCan you tell me where I can reach him?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.51,1:39:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我已经用他留下的地址找他{\r}\NI've already tried to get him at the address he gave me in Fresno.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.19,1:39:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.94,1:40:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈妈我能吃三文治吗?{\r}\NMom, may we have some sandwiches?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.94,1:40:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要在客厅拿东西吃 去厨房{\r}\NDon't take anything from the dining room. Go in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.98,1:40:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让我来拿大衣- -{\r}\NPlease go. And just leave your coats...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.53,1:40:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}祖你来招呼大家吧?{\r}\NJoe, dear, will you take care of everyone?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.03,1:40:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉!{\r}\NCharlie!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.74,1:40:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我下来了{\r}\NI'll be right down.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.74,1:40:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}啊...现在...{\r}\NWell... now... hm.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.33,1:40:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}奥克里先生 我还想香槟只在打仗时喝{\r}\NNow, Mr Oakley. I thought champagne was only for battleships!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.50,1:40:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我和妻子都不要了 你们喝吧{\r}\NNone for me, nor I'm sure, for my wife. But we hope you'll all forget we're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.34,1:40:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让我们来干杯- -  查莉还没下来吗?{\r}\NI'd like to propose a toast to... Isn't Charlie coming down?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.72,1:40:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她就下来了波特太太{\r}\NShe'll be down in a moment. Mrs Potter.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.81,1:40:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别吃那个 我弄马铃薯仅为了调味{\r}\NNot that one. Why do I make tomato? They always soak through the bread.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.77,1:41:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}试这个有小麦面包 奶油和辣椒{\r}\NTry one of these. It's whole wheat bread and cream cheese. Paprika makes it pink.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.69,1:41:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 格林先生 - 格林太太你呢?{\r}\N- Mr Greene. - Mrs Greene, what would you like?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.24,1:41:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.11,1:41:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我也要干杯 - 艾玛{\r}\N- I think I'd like to propose a toast, too. - Emmy.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.20,1:41:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为我们的访客 近年来最好的演讲者{\r}\NTo our distinguished visitor, who made the best speech heard in town for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.58,1:41:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为奥克里先生干杯{\r}\NTo that very good fellow, Mr Oakley.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.92,1:41:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 贺比 - 谢谢{\r}\N- Herbie. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.63,1:41:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们没有什么 美国的演讲者{\r}\NWe don ' t get many American speakers.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.80,1:41:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也许外来的才是最好的{\r}\NSeems like foreigners make the best talkers.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.76,1:41:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}啊她来了我们来干杯{\r}\NAh, here she is. Now for my toast.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.56,1:41:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉...{\r}\NCharlie...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.40,1:41:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你来得正好{\r}\NYou're just in time for a farewell toast.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.90,1:41:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不得不宣布 明天我会离开这{\r}\NI hate to break the news to you like this, but tomorrow I must leave Santa Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.12,1:41:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 暂时离开 - 真巧合{\r}\N- Not forever. - If that isn't the strangest coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.45,1:41:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我明天准备去三藩市 - 查理{\r}\N- I'm off to San Francisco. - Charles?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.71,1:42:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}噢艾玛 我也不想打扰大家的雅兴{\r}\NOh, Emmy darling, I didn't mean to spoil your fun tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.75,1:42:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我收到通知 明早要赶火车{\r}\NI got a letter today. I have to catch the early morning train.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.51,1:42:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}艾玛我会想念你{\r}\NI'll miss you, Emmy.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.26,1:42:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我觉得这个小镇的人...{\r}\NBut I want you all to know I'll always think of this lovely town...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.81,1:42:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}都很热情好客...{\r}\Nas a place of hospitality and kindness...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.90,1:42:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}令我有家的温暖...家{\r}\Nand homes... homes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.07,1:42:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 查理我不想你走 - 艾玛我会回来的{\r}\N- But I can't bear it if you go, Charles. - Oh, Emmy, I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.03,1:42:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我还有建造 孩子们的医院呢{\r}\NI've arranged with Dr Phillips for our little memorial for the children.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.83,1:42:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不是你要做什么{\r}\NIt isn't any of the things you've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.88,1:42:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只是我们好不容易才一起!{\r}\NIt's just the idea that we were together again. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.59,1:42:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们从小相依为命{\r}\NBut you see, we were so close growing up.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.76,1:42:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}后来查理走了我嫁人了- -{\r}\NAnd then Charles went away, and I got married, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.60,1:42:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大家都知道后来怎样{\r}\NThen, you know how it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.19,1:43:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}身为人妻 就变得很健忘了- -{\r}\NYou sort of forget you're you. You're your husband's wife...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.36,1:43:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们把你看成 是这里的一分子{\r}\NWe'll be looking for you. We feel you're one of us, don't we, Margaret?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.65,1:43:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是啊你也是俱乐部的成员{\r}\NIndeed. I want to thank you on behalf of our club.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.45,1:43:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很感谢你给医院的礼物{\r}\NAnd bless you for your gift to our hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.66,1:43:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 孩子们以后会感激你的 - 谢谢你{\r}\N- The children will bless you, too. - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.46,1:43:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}打扰了但我 我听到火车来了{\r}\NExcuse me, sir, but I-I can hear the train coming now.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.17,1:43:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不好意思{\r}\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.56,1:43:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查理上车吧{\r}\NBetter get aboard, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.85,1:43:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大家后会有期 罗杰安妮跟我来{\r}\NAlright. Goodbye, everybody. Roger, Ann, come see the train.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.73,1:43:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉来啊{\r}\NCome on, Charlie. You can see they get off.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.73,1:43:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好吧{\r}\NAlright.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.78,1:43:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想看看包厢{\r}\NI want to see the rooms, the private ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.20,1:43:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我见过卧铺 还睡过上层呢{\r}\NI've seen berths. I've slept in two uppers and one lower with papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.37,1:43:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 再见祖 - 再见查理{\r}\N- Goodbye, Joe. - Goodbye, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.33,1:44:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 再见艾玛 - 再见记得写信!{\r}\N- Goodbye, Emmy. - Goodbye. And don't forget to write!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.79,1:44:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会的你也要啊{\r}\NI will. You write too. I'll send you my address.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.05,1:44:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再见{\r}\NGoodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.39,1:44:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要在座位上跳来跳去{\r}\NDon't jump on the seats, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.31,1:44:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}佳家高清，国内最全最新高清影视资源库就在您身边！ 请加QQ：1073737340获取最新高清影视目录，谢谢！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.68,1:44:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}罗杰听到吗?{\r}\NRoger, what did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.40,1:44:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还有一个箱子 能帮我拿来吗?{\r}\NPorter, there's one more bag in the other car. Will you get it, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.36,1:44:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉车要开了 我可不想留下来{\r}\NCharlie, the train's going to start. I don't want to get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.78,1:44:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}太迟了! 我要快点下去!{\r}\NMaybe it's too late! Maybe I'll have to go along!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.74,1:44:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们就跟着来{\r}\NThere's plenty of time. You run along, we'll follow.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.08,1:44:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉{\r}\NCharlie.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.54,1:44:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}等等{\r}\NJust a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.87,1:44:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想告诉你 让我离开是明智的{\r}\NI want you to know I think you were right to make me leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.05,1:44:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为你妈妈，对大家都好{\r}\NIt's best for your mother, best for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.93,1:44:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你看到昨晚她的反应了{\r}\NYou saw what happened to her last night.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.14,1:45:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她不够坚强 我想她不能承受这打击{\r}\NShe's not very strong, you know. I don't think she could stand the shock.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.06,1:45:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 记得当她还是个孩子 - 火车开了!{\r}\N- I remember once, when she was little - - The train's moving!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.44,1:45:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听着查莉，忘记我的过去{\r}\NListen, Charlie. I want you to forget all about me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.94,1:45:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}忘记所有{\r}\NForget that I ever came to Santa Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.11,1:45:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你的手!{\r}\NYour hands!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.91,1:45:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查理叔叔 放手!让我走!{\r}\NLet me go, Uncle Charlie! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.46,1:45:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}查莉我不想的{\r}\NI've got to do this, Charlie...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.87,1:45:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但你知道的太多了{\r}\Nso long as you know what you do about me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.43,1:45:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没到时候等车再快点{\r}\NNot yet, Charlie. Let it get a little faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.73,1:45:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再快点{\r}\NJust a little faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.48,1:45:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快点{\r}\NFaster.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.98,1:45:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在!{\r}\NNow!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.26,1:46:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}圣罗莎失去了一个好儿子{\r}\NSanta Rosa has gained and lost a son,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.72,1:46:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一个她引以为荣的儿子{\r}\Na son that she can be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.39,1:46:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}勇敢慷慨善良 优秀的人格{\r}\NBrave, generous, kindly. With all of the spendid dignity -
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.23,1:46:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}杰克你来了真好{\r}\NI'm glad you were able to come, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.44,1:46:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想找人倾诉{\r}\NI couldn't have faced it without someone who knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.94,1:46:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 我知道很多但不能对你说 - 我明白{\r}\N- I did know more. I couldn't tell you. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.03,1:46:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他认为这世界是很可怕的{\r}\NHe thought the world was a horrible place.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.70,1:46:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}- 他从来没有快乐过 - 没有{\r}\N- He couldn't have been very happy ever. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.25,1:46:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他不相信身边任何人{\r}\NHe didn't trust people. He seemed to hate them.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.59,1:46:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他憎恨这个世界{\r}\NHe hated the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.42,1:47:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他说过，像我们这样的人...{\r}\NYou know, he said that people like us
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.01,1:47:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不知道外面的世界是怎样{\r}\Nhad no idea what the world was really like.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.27,1:47:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也不是那么糟糕{\r}\NWell, it's not quite as bad as that,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.39,1:47:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只是做人要留个心眼{\r}\Nbut sometimes it needs a lot of watching.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.40,1:47:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有时人也会走向极端{\r}\NIt seems to go crazy every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.52,1:47:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}像你的查理叔叔{\r}\NLike your Uncle Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.78,1:47:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他高尚的灵魂讨人喜欢的性格，永远与我们同在{\r}\NThe beauty of their souls, and characters live on with us forever.



